                Kv = null;
                const n = new Set();
                for (; n.size < 10; ) n.add(Math.floor(Math.random() * 40) + 1);
                const r = Array.from(n),
                  s = Math.random();
                let i = [...r];
                s < 0.33 ? (i = Ch(r, !0)) : s < 0.66 && (i = Ch(r, !1)),
                  t({
                    autoSelectNumbers: i,
                  });
              }
            }, 50);
        },
        clearSelections: () => {
          t({
            selectedNumbers: [],
            autoSelectNumbers: [],
          });
        },
        setIsDrawingComplete: (n) =>
          t({
            isDrawingComplete: n,
          }),
        setRiskLevel: (n) =>
          t({
            riskLevel: n,
          }),
        resetGame: () =>
          t((n) =>
            F(C({}, aS), {
              selectedNumbers: n.selectedNumbers,
              riskLevel: n.riskLevel,
            }),
          ),
        endGame: () =>
          t(() => ({
            isEnded: !0,
          })),
        setErrors: (n) =>
          t({
            errors: n,
          }),
        validateSelectedNumbers: () => {
          try {
            return (
              Nq.parse(e().selectedNumbers),
              t((n) => ({
                errors: F(C({}, n.errors), {
                  selectedNumbers: void 0,
                }),
              })),
              !0
            );
          } catch (n) {
            return (
              n instanceof ft.ZodError &&
                t((r) => {
                  var s;
                  return {
                    errors: F(C({}, r.errors), {
                      selectedNumbers:
                        (s = n.issues[0]) == null ? void 0 : s.message,
                    }),
                  };
                }),
              !1
            );
          }
        },
      }),
    );
  function lS(t, e, n) {
    return Array.from(
      {
        length: n,
      },
      (r, s) => ({
        r: Math.round(t.r + ((e.r - t.r) / (n - 1)) * s),
        g: Math.round(t.g + ((e.g - t.g) / (n - 1)) * s),
        b: Math.round(t.b + ((e.b - t.b) / (n - 1)) * s),
      }),
    );
  }
  function Aq(t) {
    {
      const e = t + 1,
        n = e % 2 === 0,
        r = Math.ceil(e / 2),
        s = lS(
          {
            r: 232,
            g: 64,
            b: 49,
          },
          {
            r: 232,
            g: 177,
            b: 49,
          },
          r,
        ).map(({ r: o, g: a, b: l }) => `rgb(${o}, ${a}, ${l})`),
        i = lS(
          {
            r: 166,
            g: 0,
            b: 4,
          },
          {
            r: 171,
            g: 121,
            b: 0,
          },
          r,
        ).map(({ r: o, g: a, b: l }) => `rgb(${o}, ${a}, ${l})`);
      return {
        background: [...s, ...s.toReversed().slice(n ? 0 : 1)],
        shadow: [...i, ...i.toReversed().slice(n ? 0 : 1)],
      };
    }
  }

    (t, e) => ((t[e] = Aq(e)), t),

  );

        "16_16": [387.0447239368574],
      },
      metadata: {
        minRow: 8,
        maxRow: 16,
        bins: 17,
      },
    },
    uS = {
      rowCount: 12,
      riskLevel: qi.MEDIUM,
      activeBalls: [],
      pendingBalls: [],
      activeRound: null,
      isDropping: !1,
      betAmount: 10,
      autoPlayCount: 0,
      lastLandingBin: null,
      plinkoBalance: 0,
      ballPositions: [],
      numberOfBalls: 1,
      multiplierFeed: [],
    },
    dS = (t) => t,
    Mq = (t, e, n, r) => {
      const s = yl[n][r],
        i = t;
      return i >= 0 && i < s.length ? Math.abs(s[i] - e) < 0.01 : !1;
    },
    Sn = nr((t, e) =>
      F(C({}, uS), {
        setNumberOfBalls: (n) =>
          t({
            numberOfBalls: n,
          }),
        setRowCount: (n) =>
          t({
            rowCount: n,
          }),
        setRiskLevel: (n) =>
          t({
            riskLevel: n,
          }),
        setBetAmount: (n) =>
          t({
            betAmount: n,
          }),
        setPlinkoBalance: (n) =>
          t({
            plinkoBalance: n,
          }),
        getAnimationDuration: () => {
          const n = e(),
            r = 1600,
            s = 2800,
            i = 8;
          return Math.floor(r + ((n.rowCount - i) * (s - r)) / (16 - i));
        },
        addBall: (n) => {
          const r = e(),
            s = Number(n.path);
          Mq(s, n.multiplier, r.rowCount, r.riskLevel) ||
            console.warn(
              "Ball multiplier does not match expected landing position",
            );
          const o = F(C({}, n), {
            landingPosition: s,
            isDropping: !0,
          });
          t((a) => ({
            activeBalls: [...a.activeBalls, o],
          }));
        },
        removeBall: (n) => {
          t((r) => ({
            activeBalls: r.activeBalls.filter((s) => s.id !== n),
            lastLandingBin: null,
          }));
        },
        setIsDropping: (n) =>
          t({
            isDropping: n,
          }),
        setActiveRound: (n) => {
          var s, i;
          const r = n.paths.map((o) =>
            F(C({}, o), {
              landingPosition: dS(o.path),
              isDropping: !1,
            }),
          );
          t({
            activeRound: F(C({}, n), {
              paths: r,
              slot:
                (i = (s = r[0]) == null ? void 0 : s.landingPosition) != null
                  ? i
                  : null,
            }),
          });
        },
        setAutoPlayCount: (n) =>
          t({
            autoPlayCount: n,
          }),
        resetGame: () =>
          t((n) =>
            F(C({}, uS), {
              betAmount: n.betAmount,
              riskLevel: n.riskLevel,
              rowCount: n.rowCount,
            }),
          ),
        updateBallComplete: (n) => {
          const r = e(),
            s = r.activeBalls.find((i) => i.id === n);
          if ((s == null ? void 0 : s.landingPosition) !== void 0) {
            yl[r.rowCount][r.riskLevel];
            const i = s.landingPosition;
            t({
              lastLandingBin: i,
              activeBalls: r.activeBalls.map((o) =>
                o.id === n
                  ? F(C({}, o), {
                      isComplete: !0,
                    })
                  : o,
              ),
            });
          }
        },
        calculateLandingPosition: (n) => dS(n),
        setLastLandingBin: (n) =>
          t({
            lastLandingBin: n,
          }),
        addBallPosition: (n) =>
          t((r) => ({
            ballPositions: [...r.ballPositions, n],
          })),
        clearBallPositions: () =>
          t({
            ballPositions: [],
          }),
        getBallPositions: () => e().ballPositions,
        clearActiveBalls: () =>
          t({
            activeBalls: [],
          }),
        plinkoWinFeedData: (n, r) =>
          t((s) => {
            const i = [
              ...s.multiplierFeed,
              {
                multiplier: n,
                roundId: r,
              },
            ];
            return (
              i.length > 20 && i.splice(0, i.length - 20),
              {
                multiplierFeed: i,
              }
            );
          }),
      }),
    ),
    Xv = [10, 20, 30, 40, 50],
    fS = {
      segmentCount: 20,
      risk: "medium",
      betResult: null,
      spinTarget: null,
      isWin: !1,
      isSpinning: !1,
      isSpinComplete: !1,
      winAmount: 0,
      currentMultiplier: "0.0x",
      wheelSegments: [],
      selectedMultiplier: "1.5x",
      errors: {},
      wheelTargetData: null,
      highlightedMultiplier: null,
      showConfetti: !1,
    },
    Lu = nr((t, e) =>
      F(C({}, fS), {
        setSegmentCount: (n) => {
          t({
            segmentCount: n,
          }),
            t((r) => ({
              errors: F(C({}, r.errors), {
                segmentCount: void 0,
              }),
            }));
        },
        setRisk: (n) =>
          t({
            risk: n,
          }),
        setBetResult: (n) =>
          t({
            betResult: n,
          }),
        setIsWin: (n) =>
          t({
            isWin: n,
          }),
        setIsSpinning: (n) =>
          t({
            isSpinning: n,
          }),
        setIsSpinComplete: (n) =>
          t({
            isSpinComplete: n,
          }),
        setWinAmount: (n) =>
          t({
            winAmount: n,
          }),
        setCurrentMultiplier: (n) =>
          t({
            currentMultiplier: n,
          }),
        setWheelSegments: (n) =>
          t({
            wheelSegments: n,
          }),
        setSelectedMultiplier: (n) =>
          t({
            selectedMultiplier: n,
          }),
        setErrors: (n) =>
          t({
            errors: n,
          }),
        setWheelTargetData: (n) =>
          t({
            wheelTargetData: n,
          }),
        setSpinTarget: (n) =>
          t({
            spinTarget: n,
          }),
        setHighlightedMultiplier: (n) =>
          t({
            highlightedMultiplier: n,
          }),
        setShowConfetti: (n) =>
          t({
            showConfetti: n,
          }),
        validateSegmentCount: () =>
          Xv.includes(e().segmentCount)
            ? (t((n) => ({
                errors: F(C({}, n.errors), {
                  segmentCount: void 0,
                }),
              })),
              !0)
            : (t((n) => ({
                errors: F(C({}, n.errors), {
                  segmentCount: "Invalid segment count",
                }),
              })),
              !1),
        resetGame: () =>
          t(
            F(C({}, fS), {
              segmentCount: e().segmentCount,
              risk: e().risk,
              selectedMultiplier: e().selectedMultiplier,
              wheelSegments: e().wheelSegments,
            }),
          ),
      }),

          const y = Math.floor(h / v) * v,
            x = Math.ceil(h / v) * v,
            w = (h - y) / h,
            _ = (x - h) / h;

    function M(D) {

        U = D.spread * (Math.PI / 180);

        x: D.x,

        velocity: D.startVelocity * 0.5 + Math.random() * D.startVelocity,

    function j(D, R) {
      (R.x += Math.cos(R.angle2D) * R.velocity + R.drift),
        (R.y += Math.sin(R.angle2D) * R.velocity + R.gravity),

      var U = R.tick++ / R.totalTicks,
        G = R.x + R.random * R.tiltCos,

      return D.closePath(), D.fill(), R.tick < R.totalTicks;
    }

  function OY(t) {

  function AK(t, e) {
    const n = Math.abs(e.top - t.y),
      r = Math.abs(e.bottom - t.y),
      s = Math.abs(e.right - t.x),
      i = Math.abs(e.left - t.x);
    switch (Math.min(n, r, s, i)) {
      case i:
        return "left";
      case s:
        return "right";
      case n:
        return "top";
      case r:
        return "bottom";
      default:
        throw new Error("unreachable");
    }
  }
  function jK(t, e, n = 5) {
    const r = [];
    switch (e) {
      case "top":
        r.push(
          {
            x: t.x - n,
            y: t.y + n,
          },
          {
            x: t.x + n,
            y: t.y + n,
          },
        );
        break;
      case "bottom":
        r.push(
          {
            x: t.x - n,
            y: t.y - n,
          },
          {
            x: t.x + n,
            y: t.y - n,
          },
        );
        break;
      case "left":
        r.push(
          {
            x: t.x + n,
            y: t.y - n,
          },
          {
            x: t.x + n,
            y: t.y + n,
          },
        );
        break;
      case "right":
        r.push(
          {
            x: t.x - n,
            y: t.y - n,
          },
          {
            x: t.x - n,
            y: t.y + n,
          },
        );
        break;
    }
    return r;
  }
  function MK(t) {
    const { top: e, right: n, bottom: r, left: s } = t;
    return [
      {
        x: s,
        y: e,
      },
      {
        x: n,
        y: e,
      },
      {
        x: n,
        y: r,
      },
      {
        x: s,
        y: r,
      },
    ];
  }
  function OK(t, e) {
    const { x: n, y: r } = t;
    let s = !1;
    for (let i = 0, o = e.length - 1; i < e.length; o = i++) {
      const a = e[i].x,
        l = e[i].y,
        c = e[o].x,
        u = e[o].y;
      l > r != u > r && n < ((c - a) * (r - l)) / (u - l) + a && (s = !s);
    }
    return s;
  }
  function IK(t) {
    const e = t.slice();
    return (
      e.sort((n, r) =>
        n.x < r.x ? -1 : n.x > r.x ? 1 : n.y < r.y ? -1 : n.y > r.y ? 1 : 0,
      ),
      DK(e)
    );
  }
  function DK(t) {
    if (t.length <= 1) return t.slice();
    const e = [];
    for (let r = 0; r < t.length; r++) {
      const s = t[r];
      for (; e.length >= 2; ) {
        const i = e[e.length - 1],
          o = e[e.length - 2];
        if ((i.x - o.x) * (s.y - o.y) >= (i.y - o.y) * (s.x - o.x)) e.pop();
        else break;
      }
      e.push(s);
    }
    e.pop();
    const n = [];
    for (let r = t.length - 1; r >= 0; r--) {
      const s = t[r];
      for (; n.length >= 2; ) {

          o = n[n.length - 2];

  function pr({

  const hn = k.forwardRef((s, r) => {

    return t ? parseInt(t, 10) : 0;
  }
  function EP(t, e) {
    const n = t / e;
    return isNaN(n) ? 0 : n;
  }
  function xp(t) {
    const e = EP(t.viewport, t.content),
      n = t.scrollbar.paddingStart + t.scrollbar.paddingEnd,
      r = (t.scrollbar.size - n) * e;
    return Math.max(r, 18);
  }
  function gQ(t, e, n, r = "ltr") {
    const s = xp(n),
      i = s / 2,

      c = n.scrollbar.size - n.scrollbar.paddingEnd - a,
      u = n.content - n.viewport,
      f = r === "ltr" ? [0, u] : [u * -1, 0];

  }
  function NP(t, e, n = "ltr") {

      s = e.scrollbar.paddingStart + e.scrollbar.paddingEnd,
      i = e.scrollbar.size - s,
      o = e.content - e.viewport,
      a = i - r,
      l = n === "ltr" ? [0, o] : [o * -1, 0],
      c = Hu(t, l);

  }
  function AP(t, e) {
    return (n) => {
      if (t[0] === t[1] || e[0] === e[1]) return e[0];
      const r = (e[1] - e[0]) / (t[1] - t[0]);
      return e[0] + r * (n - t[0]);
    };
  }
  function jP(t, e) {
    return t > 0 && t < e;
  }

                  return (c._chained = o), c;
                }),
                (s.chainPathBefore = function (o, a, l) {
                  return s.set(o, a, s.chain(l, s.get(o, a)));
                }),
                (s.chainPathAfter = function (o, a, l) {
                  return s.set(o, a, s.chain(s.get(o, a), l));

                  s._decomp = o;

        function (n, r) {
          var s = {};
          (n.exports = s),
            (function () {

                  },

        function (n, r) {
          var s = {};
          (n.exports = s),
            (function () {
              (s.create = function (i, o) {
                return {
                  x: i || 0,
                  y: o || 0,
                };
              }),
                (s.clone = function (i) {
                  return {
                    x: i.x,
                    y: i.y,
                  };
                }),
                (s.magnitude = function (i) {
                  return Math.sqrt(i.x * i.x + i.y * i.y);
                }),
                (s.magnitudeSquared = function (i) {
                  return i.x * i.x + i.y * i.y;
                }),
                (s.rotate = function (i, o, a) {
                  var l = Math.cos(o),
                    c = Math.sin(o);
                  a || (a = {});
                  var u = i.x * l - i.y * c;
                  return (a.y = i.x * c + i.y * l), (a.x = u), a;
                }),
                (s.rotateAbout = function (i, o, a, l) {
                  var c = Math.cos(o),
                    u = Math.sin(o);
                  l || (l = {});

                  return (
                    (l.y = a.y + ((i.x - a.x) * u + (i.y - a.y) * c)),
                    (l.x = f),
                    l
                  );
                }),
                (s.normalise = function (i) {
                  var o = s.magnitude(i);
                  return o === 0
                    ? {
                        x: 0,
                        y: 0,
                      }
                    : {
                        x: i.x / o,
                        y: i.y / o,
                      };
                }),
                (s.dot = function (i, o) {
                  return i.x * o.x + i.y * o.y;
                }),
                (s.cross = function (i, o) {
                  return i.x * o.y - i.y * o.x;
                }),
                (s.cross3 = function (i, o, a) {
                  return (o.x - i.x) * (a.y - i.y) - (o.y - i.y) * (a.x - i.x);
                }),
                (s.add = function (i, o, a) {
                  return a || (a = {}), (a.x = i.x + o.x), (a.y = i.y + o.y), a;
                }),
                (s.sub = function (i, o, a) {
                  return a || (a = {}), (a.x = i.x - o.x), (a.y = i.y - o.y), a;
                }),
                (s.mult = function (i, o) {
                  return {
                    x: i.x * o,
                    y: i.y * o,
                  };
                }),
                (s.div = function (i, o) {
                  return {
                    x: i.x / o,
                    y: i.y / o,
                  };
                }),
                (s.perp = function (i, o) {
                  return (
                    (o = o === !0 ? -1 : 1),
                    {
                      x: o * -i.y,
                      y: o * i.x,
                    }
                  );
                }),
                (s.neg = function (i) {
                  return {
                    x: -i.x,
                    y: -i.y,
                  };
                }),
                (s.angle = function (i, o) {
                  return Math.atan2(o.y - i.y, o.x - i.x);
                }),
                (s._temp = [
                  s.create(),
                  s.create(),
                  s.create(),
                  s.create(),
                  s.create(),
                  s.create(),
                ]);
            })();

        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(2),
            a = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (l, c) {
              for (var u = [], f = 0; f < l.length; f++) {
                var h = l[f],
                  p = {
                    x: h.x,
                    y: h.y,
                    index: f,
                    body: c,
                    isInternal: !1,
                  };
                u.push(p);
              }
              return u;
            }),
              (i.fromPath = function (l, c) {
                var u = /L?\s*([-\d.e]+)[\s,]*([-\d.e]+)*/gi,
                  f = [];
                return (
                  l.replace(u, function (h, p, g) {
                    f.push({
                      x: parseFloat(p),
                      y: parseFloat(g),
                    });
                  }),
                  i.create(f, c)
                );
              }),
              (i.centre = function (l) {
                for (
                  var c = i.area(l, !0),
                    u = {
                      x: 0,
                      y: 0,
                    },
                    f,
                    h,
                    p,
                    g = 0;
                  g < l.length;
                  g++
                )
                  (p = (g + 1) % l.length),
                    (f = o.cross(l[g], l[p])),
                    (h = o.mult(o.add(l[g], l[p]), f)),
                    (u = o.add(u, h));
                return o.div(u, 6 * c);
              }),
              (i.mean = function (l) {
                for (
                  var c = {
                      x: 0,
                      y: 0,
                    },
                    u = 0;
                  u < l.length;
                  u++
                )
                  (c.x += l[u].x), (c.y += l[u].y);
                return o.div(c, l.length);
              }),
              (i.area = function (l, c) {
                for (var u = 0, f = l.length - 1, h = 0; h < l.length; h++)
                  (u += (l[f].x - l[h].x) * (l[f].y + l[h].y)), (f = h);
                return c ? u / 2 : Math.abs(u) / 2;
              }),
              (i.inertia = function (l, c) {
                for (var u = 0, f = 0, h = l, p, g, m = 0; m < h.length; m++)
                  (g = (m + 1) % h.length),
                    (p = Math.abs(o.cross(h[g], h[m]))),
                    (u +=
                      p *
                      (o.dot(h[g], h[g]) +
                        o.dot(h[g], h[m]) +
                        o.dot(h[m], h[m]))),
                    (f += p);
                return (c / 6) * (u / f);
              }),
              (i.translate = function (l, c, u) {
                u = typeof u != "undefined" ? u : 1;
                var f = l.length,
                  h = c.x * u,
                  p = c.y * u,
                  g;
                for (g = 0; g < f; g++) (l[g].x += h), (l[g].y += p);
                return l;
              }),
              (i.rotate = function (l, c, u) {
                if (c !== 0) {
                  var f = Math.cos(c),
                    h = Math.sin(c),
                    p = u.x,
                    g = u.y,
                    m = l.length,
                    v,
                    y,
                    x,
                    w;
                  for (w = 0; w < m; w++)
                    (v = l[w]),
                      (y = v.x - p),
                      (x = v.y - g),
                      (v.x = p + (y * f - x * h)),
                      (v.y = g + (y * h + x * f));
                  return l;
                }
              }),
              (i.contains = function (l, c) {
                for (
                  var u = c.x, f = c.y, h = l.length, p = l[h - 1], g, m = 0;
                  m < h;
                  m++
                ) {
                  if (
                    ((g = l[m]),
                    (u - p.x) * (g.y - p.y) + (f - p.y) * (p.x - g.x) > 0)
                  )
                    return !1;
                  p = g;
                }
                return !0;
              }),
              (i.scale = function (l, c, u, f) {
                if (c === 1 && u === 1) return l;
                f = f || i.centre(l);
                for (var h, p, g = 0; g < l.length; g++)
                  (h = l[g]),
                    (p = o.sub(h, f)),
                    (l[g].x = f.x + p.x * c),
                    (l[g].y = f.y + p.y * u);
                return l;
              }),
              (i.chamfer = function (l, c, u, f, h) {
                typeof c == "number" ? (c = [c]) : (c = c || [8]),
                  (u = typeof u != "undefined" ? u : -1),
                  (f = f || 2),
                  (h = h || 14);
                for (var p = [], g = 0; g < l.length; g++) {
                  var m = l[g - 1 >= 0 ? g - 1 : l.length - 1],
                    v = l[g],
                    y = l[(g + 1) % l.length],
                    x = c[g < c.length ? g : c.length - 1];
                  if (x === 0) {
                    p.push(v);
                    continue;
                  }
                  var w = o.normalise({
                      x: v.y - m.y,
                      y: m.x - v.x,
                    }),
                    _ = o.normalise({
                      x: y.y - v.y,
                      y: v.x - y.x,
                    }),
                    b = Math.sqrt(2 * Math.pow(x, 2)),
                    T = o.mult(a.clone(w), x),
                    E = o.normalise(o.mult(o.add(w, _), 0.5)),
                    P = o.sub(v, o.mult(E, b)),
                    N = u;
                  u === -1 && (N = Math.pow(x, 0.32) * 1.75),
                    (N = a.clamp(N, f, h)),
                    N % 2 === 1 && (N += 1);
                  for (
                    var A = Math.acos(o.dot(w, _)), M = A / N, j = 0;
                    j < N;
                    j++
                  )
                    p.push(o.add(o.rotate(T, M * j), P));
                }
                return p;
              }),
              (i.clockwiseSort = function (l) {
                var c = i.mean(l);
                return (
                  l.sort(function (u, f) {
                    return o.angle(c, u) - o.angle(c, f);
                  }),
                  l
                );
              }),
              (i.isConvex = function (l) {
                var c = 0,
                  u = l.length,
                  f,
                  h,
                  p,
                  g;
                if (u < 3) return null;
                for (f = 0; f < u; f++)
                  if (
                    ((h = (f + 1) % u),
                    (p = (f + 2) % u),
                    (g = (l[h].x - l[f].x) * (l[p].y - l[h].y)),
                    (g -= (l[h].y - l[f].y) * (l[p].x - l[h].x)),
                    g < 0 ? (c |= 1) : g > 0 && (c |= 2),
                    c === 3)
                  )
                    return !1;
                return c !== 0 ? !0 : null;
              }),
              (i.hull = function (l) {
                var c = [],
                  u = [],
                  f,
                  h;
                for (
                  l = l.slice(0),
                    l.sort(function (p, g) {
                      var m = p.x - g.x;
                      return m !== 0 ? m : p.y - g.y;
                    }),
                    h = 0;
                  h < l.length;
                  h += 1
                ) {
                  for (
                    f = l[h];
                    u.length >= 2 &&
                    o.cross3(u[u.length - 2], u[u.length - 1], f) <= 0;

                  )
                    u.pop();
                  u.push(f);
                }
                for (h = l.length - 1; h >= 0; h -= 1) {
                  for (
                    f = l[h];
                    c.length >= 2 &&
                    o.cross3(c[c.length - 2], c[c.length - 1], f) <= 0;

                  )
                    c.pop();
                  c.push(f);
                }
                return c.pop(), u.pop(), c.concat(u);
              });
          })();
        },

                  ? ((p.positionPrev.x += g.x),
                    (p.positionPrev.y += g.y),
                    (p.position.x += g.x),
                    (p.position.y += g.y))
                  : ((p.positionPrev.x =
                      g.x - (p.position.x - p.positionPrev.x)),
                    (p.positionPrev.y =
                      g.y - (p.position.y - p.positionPrev.y)),
                    (p.position.x = g.x),
                    (p.position.y = g.y));
              }),
              (i.setPosition = function (p, g, m) {
                var v = a.sub(g, p.position);
                m
                  ? ((p.positionPrev.x = p.position.x),
                    (p.positionPrev.y = p.position.y),
                    (p.velocity.x = v.x),
                    (p.velocity.y = v.y),
                    (p.speed = a.magnitude(v)))
                  : ((p.positionPrev.x += v.x), (p.positionPrev.y += v.y));
                for (var y = 0; y < p.parts.length; y++) {
                  var x = p.parts[y];
                  (x.position.x += v.x),
                    (x.position.y += v.y),
                    o.translate(x.vertices, v),
                    u.update(x.bounds, x.vertices, p.velocity);
                }
              }),
              (i.setAngle = function (p, g, m) {
                var v = g - p.angle;
                m
                  ? ((p.anglePrev = p.angle),
                    (p.angularVelocity = v),
                    (p.angularSpeed = Math.abs(v)))
                  : (p.anglePrev += v);
                for (var y = 0; y < p.parts.length; y++) {
                  var x = p.parts[y];
                  (x.angle += v),
                    o.rotate(x.vertices, v, p.position),
                    f.rotate(x.axes, v),
                    u.update(x.bounds, x.vertices, p.velocity),
                    y > 0 &&
                      a.rotateAbout(x.position, v, p.position, x.position);
                }
              }),
              (i.setVelocity = function (p, g) {
                var m = p.deltaTime / i._baseDelta;
                (p.positionPrev.x = p.position.x - g.x * m),
                  (p.positionPrev.y = p.position.y - g.y * m),
                  (p.velocity.x = (p.position.x - p.positionPrev.x) / m),
                  (p.velocity.y = (p.position.y - p.positionPrev.y) / m),
                  (p.speed = a.magnitude(p.velocity));
              }),
              (i.getVelocity = function (p) {
                var g = i._baseDelta / p.deltaTime;
                return {
                  x: (p.position.x - p.positionPrev.x) * g,
                  y: (p.position.y - p.positionPrev.y) * g,
                };
              }),
              (i.getSpeed = function (p) {
                return a.magnitude(i.getVelocity(p));
              }),
              (i.setSpeed = function (p, g) {
                i.setVelocity(p, a.mult(a.normalise(i.getVelocity(p)), g));
              }),
              (i.setAngularVelocity = function (p, g) {
                var m = p.deltaTime / i._baseDelta;
                (p.anglePrev = p.angle - g * m),
                  (p.angularVelocity = (p.angle - p.anglePrev) / m),
                  (p.angularSpeed = Math.abs(p.angularVelocity));
              }),
              (i.getAngularVelocity = function (p) {
                return ((p.angle - p.anglePrev) * i._baseDelta) / p.deltaTime;
              }),
              (i.getAngularSpeed = function (p) {
                return Math.abs(i.getAngularVelocity(p));
              }),
              (i.setAngularSpeed = function (p, g) {
                i.setAngularVelocity(p, c.sign(i.getAngularVelocity(p)) * g);
              }),
              (i.translate = function (p, g, m) {
                i.setPosition(p, a.add(p.position, g), m);
              }),
              (i.rotate = function (p, g, m, v) {
                if (!m) i.setAngle(p, p.angle + g, v);
                else {
                  var y = Math.cos(g),
                    x = Math.sin(g),
                    w = p.position.x - m.x,
                    _ = p.position.y - m.y;
                  i.setPosition(
                    p,
                    {
                      x: m.x + (w * y - _ * x),
                      y: m.y + (w * x + _ * y),
                    },
                    v,
                  ),
                    i.setAngle(p, p.angle + g, v);
                }
              }),
              (i.scale = function (p, g, m, v) {
                var y = 0,
                  x = 0;
                v = v || p.position;
                for (var w = 0; w < p.parts.length; w++) {
                  var _ = p.parts[w];
                  o.scale(_.vertices, g, m, v),
                    (_.axes = f.fromVertices(_.vertices)),
                    (_.area = o.area(_.vertices)),
                    i.setMass(_, p.density * _.area),
                    o.translate(_.vertices, {
                      x: -_.position.x,
                      y: -_.position.y,
                    }),
                    i.setInertia(
                      _,
                      i._inertiaScale * o.inertia(_.vertices, _.mass),
                    ),
                    o.translate(_.vertices, {
                      x: _.position.x,
                      y: _.position.y,
                    }),
                    w > 0 && ((y += _.area), (x += _.inertia)),
                    (_.position.x = v.x + (_.position.x - v.x) * g),
                    (_.position.y = v.y + (_.position.y - v.y) * m),
                    u.update(_.bounds, _.vertices, p.velocity);
                }
                p.parts.length > 1 &&
                  ((p.area = y),
                  p.isStatic ||
                    (i.setMass(p, p.density * y), i.setInertia(p, x))),
                  p.circleRadius &&
                    (g === m ? (p.circleRadius *= g) : (p.circleRadius = null));
              }),
              (i.update = function (p, g) {
                g = (typeof g != "undefined" ? g : 1e3 / 60) * p.timeScale;
                var m = g * g,
                  v = i._timeCorrection ? g / (p.deltaTime || g) : 1,
                  y = 1 - p.frictionAir * (g / c._baseDelta),
                  x = (p.position.x - p.positionPrev.x) * v,
                  w = (p.position.y - p.positionPrev.y) * v;
                (p.velocity.x = x * y + (p.force.x / p.mass) * m),
                  (p.velocity.y = w * y + (p.force.y / p.mass) * m),
                  (p.positionPrev.x = p.position.x),
                  (p.positionPrev.y = p.position.y),
                  (p.position.x += p.velocity.x),
                  (p.position.y += p.velocity.y),
                  (p.deltaTime = g),
                  (p.angularVelocity =
                    (p.angle - p.anglePrev) * y * v +
                    (p.torque / p.inertia) * m),
                  (p.anglePrev = p.angle),
                  (p.angle += p.angularVelocity);
                for (var _ = 0; _ < p.parts.length; _++) {
                  var b = p.parts[_];
                  o.translate(b.vertices, p.velocity),
                    _ > 0 &&
                      ((b.position.x += p.velocity.x),
                      (b.position.y += p.velocity.y)),
                    p.angularVelocity !== 0 &&
                      (o.rotate(b.vertices, p.angularVelocity, p.position),
                      f.rotate(b.axes, p.angularVelocity),
                      _ > 0 &&
                        a.rotateAbout(
                          b.position,
                          p.angularVelocity,
                          p.position,
                          b.position,
                        )),
                    u.update(b.bounds, b.vertices, p.velocity);
                }
              }),
              (i.updateVelocities = function (p) {
                var g = i._baseDelta / p.deltaTime,
                  m = p.velocity;
                (m.x = (p.position.x - p.positionPrev.x) * g),
                  (m.y = (p.position.y - p.positionPrev.y) * g),
                  (p.speed = Math.sqrt(m.x * m.x + m.y * m.y)),
                  (p.angularVelocity = (p.angle - p.anglePrev) * g),
                  (p.angularSpeed = Math.abs(p.angularVelocity));
              }),
              (i.applyForce = function (p, g, m) {
                var v = {
                  x: g.x - p.position.x,
                  y: g.y - p.position.y,
                };
                (p.force.x += m.x),
                  (p.force.y += m.y),
                  (p.torque += v.x * m.y - v.y * m.x);
              }),
              (i._totalProperties = function (p) {
                for (
                  var g = {
                      mass: 0,
                      area: 0,
                      inertia: 0,
                      centre: {
                        x: 0,
                        y: 0,
                      },
                    },
                    m = p.parts.length === 1 ? 0 : 1;
                  m < p.parts.length;
                  m++
                ) {
                  var v = p.parts[m],
                    y = v.mass !== 1 / 0 ? v.mass : 1;
                  (g.mass += y),
                    (g.area += v.area),
                    (g.inertia += v.inertia),
                    (g.centre = a.add(g.centre, a.mult(v.position, y)));
                }
                return (g.centre = a.div(g.centre, g.mass)), g;
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i.on = function (a, l, c) {
              for (var u = l.split(" "), f, h = 0; h < u.length; h++)
                (f = u[h]),
                  (a.events = a.events || {}),
                  (a.events[f] = a.events[f] || []),
                  a.events[f].push(c);
              return c;
            }),
              (i.off = function (a, l, c) {
                if (!l) {
                  a.events = {};
                  return;
                }
                typeof l == "function" &&
                  ((c = l), (l = o.keys(a.events).join(" ")));
                for (var u = l.split(" "), f = 0; f < u.length; f++) {
                  var h = a.events[u[f]],
                    p = [];
                  if (c && h)
                    for (var g = 0; g < h.length; g++)
                      h[g] !== c && p.push(h[g]);
                  a.events[u[f]] = p;
                }
              }),
              (i.trigger = function (a, l, c) {
                var u,
                  f,
                  h,
                  p,
                  g = a.events;
                if (g && o.keys(g).length > 0) {
                  c || (c = {}), (u = l.split(" "));
                  for (var m = 0; m < u.length; m++)
                    if (((f = u[m]), (h = g[f]), h)) {
                      (p = o.clone(c, !1)), (p.name = f), (p.source = a);
                      for (var v = 0; v < h.length; v++) h[v].apply(a, [p]);
                    }
                }
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(5),
            a = s(0),
            l = s(1),
            c = s(4);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (u) {
              return a.extend(
                {
                  id: a.nextId(),
                  type: "composite",
                  parent: null,
                  isModified: !1,
                  bodies: [],
                  constraints: [],
                  composites: [],
                  label: "Composite",
                  plugin: {},
                  cache: {
                    allBodies: null,
                    allConstraints: null,
                    allComposites: null,
                  },
                },
                u,
              );
            }),
              (i.setModified = function (u, f, h, p) {
                if (
                  ((u.isModified = f),
                  f &&
                    u.cache &&
                    ((u.cache.allBodies = null),
                    (u.cache.allConstraints = null),
                    (u.cache.allComposites = null)),
                  h && u.parent && i.setModified(u.parent, f, h, p),
                  p)
                )
                  for (var g = 0; g < u.composites.length; g++) {
                    var m = u.composites[g];
                    i.setModified(m, f, h, p);
                  }
              }),
              (i.add = function (u, f) {
                var h = [].concat(f);
                o.trigger(u, "beforeAdd", {
                  object: f,
                });
                for (var p = 0; p < h.length; p++) {
                  var g = h[p];
                  switch (g.type) {
                    case "body":
                      if (g.parent !== g) {
                        a.warn(
                          "Composite.add: skipped adding a compound body part (you must add its parent instead)",
                        );
                        break;
                      }
                      i.addBody(u, g);
                      break;
                    case "constraint":
                      i.addConstraint(u, g);
                      break;
                    case "composite":
                      i.addComposite(u, g);
                      break;
                    case "mouseConstraint":
                      i.addConstraint(u, g.constraint);
                      break;
                  }
                }
                return (
                  o.trigger(u, "afterAdd", {
                    object: f,
                  }),
                  u
                );
              }),
              (i.remove = function (u, f, h) {
                var p = [].concat(f);
                o.trigger(u, "beforeRemove", {
                  object: f,
                });
                for (var g = 0; g < p.length; g++) {
                  var m = p[g];
                  switch (m.type) {
                    case "body":
                      i.removeBody(u, m, h);
                      break;
                    case "constraint":
                      i.removeConstraint(u, m, h);
                      break;
                    case "composite":
                      i.removeComposite(u, m, h);
                      break;
                    case "mouseConstraint":
                      i.removeConstraint(u, m.constraint);
                      break;
                  }
                }
                return (
                  o.trigger(u, "afterRemove", {
                    object: f,
                  }),
                  u
                );
              }),
              (i.addComposite = function (u, f) {
                return (
                  u.composites.push(f),
                  (f.parent = u),
                  i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1),
                  u
                );
              }),
              (i.removeComposite = function (u, f, h) {
                var p = a.indexOf(u.composites, f);
                if (p !== -1) {
                  var g = i.allBodies(f);
                  i.removeCompositeAt(u, p);
                  for (var m = 0; m < g.length; m++) g[m].sleepCounter = 0;
                }
                if (h)
                  for (var m = 0; m < u.composites.length; m++)
                    i.removeComposite(u.composites[m], f, !0);
                return u;
              }),
              (i.removeCompositeAt = function (u, f) {
                return (
                  u.composites.splice(f, 1), i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1), u
                );
              }),
              (i.addBody = function (u, f) {
                return u.bodies.push(f), i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1), u;
              }),
              (i.removeBody = function (u, f, h) {
                var p = a.indexOf(u.bodies, f);
                if (
                  (p !== -1 && (i.removeBodyAt(u, p), (f.sleepCounter = 0)), h)
                )
                  for (var g = 0; g < u.composites.length; g++)
                    i.removeBody(u.composites[g], f, !0);
                return u;
              }),
              (i.removeBodyAt = function (u, f) {
                return u.bodies.splice(f, 1), i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1), u;
              }),
              (i.addConstraint = function (u, f) {
                return u.constraints.push(f), i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1), u;
              }),
              (i.removeConstraint = function (u, f, h) {
                var p = a.indexOf(u.constraints, f);
                if ((p !== -1 && i.removeConstraintAt(u, p), h))
                  for (var g = 0; g < u.composites.length; g++)
                    i.removeConstraint(u.composites[g], f, !0);
                return u;
              }),
              (i.removeConstraintAt = function (u, f) {
                return (
                  u.constraints.splice(f, 1), i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1), u
                );
              }),
              (i.clear = function (u, f, h) {
                if (h)
                  for (var p = 0; p < u.composites.length; p++)
                    i.clear(u.composites[p], f, !0);
                return (
                  f
                    ? (u.bodies = u.bodies.filter(function (g) {
                        return g.isStatic;
                      }))
                    : (u.bodies.length = 0),
                  (u.constraints.length = 0),
                  (u.composites.length = 0),
                  i.setModified(u, !0, !0, !1),
                  u
                );
              }),
              (i.allBodies = function (u) {
                if (u.cache && u.cache.allBodies) return u.cache.allBodies;
                for (
                  var f = [].concat(u.bodies), h = 0;
                  h < u.composites.length;
                  h++
                )
                  f = f.concat(i.allBodies(u.composites[h]));
                return u.cache && (u.cache.allBodies = f), f;
              }),
              (i.allConstraints = function (u) {
                if (u.cache && u.cache.allConstraints)
                  return u.cache.allConstraints;
                for (
                  var f = [].concat(u.constraints), h = 0;
                  h < u.composites.length;
                  h++
                )
                  f = f.concat(i.allConstraints(u.composites[h]));
                return u.cache && (u.cache.allConstraints = f), f;
              }),
              (i.allComposites = function (u) {
                if (u.cache && u.cache.allComposites)
                  return u.cache.allComposites;
                for (
                  var f = [].concat(u.composites), h = 0;
                  h < u.composites.length;
                  h++
                )
                  f = f.concat(i.allComposites(u.composites[h]));
                return u.cache && (u.cache.allComposites = f), f;
              }),
              (i.get = function (u, f, h) {
                var p, g;
                switch (h) {
                  case "body":
                    p = i.allBodies(u);
                    break;
                  case "constraint":
                    p = i.allConstraints(u);
                    break;
                  case "composite":
                    p = i.allComposites(u).concat(u);
                    break;
                }
                return p
                  ? ((g = p.filter(function (m) {
                      return m.id.toString() === f.toString();
                    })),
                    g.length === 0 ? null : g[0])
                  : null;
              }),
              (i.move = function (u, f, h) {
                return i.remove(u, f), i.add(h, f), u;
              }),
              (i.rebase = function (u) {
                for (
                  var f = i
                      .allBodies(u)
                      .concat(i.allConstraints(u))
                      .concat(i.allComposites(u)),
                    h = 0;
                  h < f.length;
                  h++
                )
                  f[h].id = a.nextId();
                return u;
              }),
              (i.translate = function (u, f, h) {
                for (
                  var p = h ? i.allBodies(u) : u.bodies, g = 0;
                  g < p.length;
                  g++
                )
                  c.translate(p[g], f);
                return u;
              }),
              (i.rotate = function (u, f, h, p) {
                for (
                  var g = Math.cos(f),
                    m = Math.sin(f),
                    v = p ? i.allBodies(u) : u.bodies,
                    y = 0;
                  y < v.length;
                  y++
                ) {
                  var x = v[y],
                    w = x.position.x - h.x,
                    _ = x.position.y - h.y;
                  c.setPosition(x, {
                    x: h.x + (w * g - _ * m),
                    y: h.y + (w * m + _ * g),
                  }),
                    c.rotate(x, f);
                }
                return u;
              }),
              (i.scale = function (u, f, h, p, g) {
                for (
                  var m = g ? i.allBodies(u) : u.bodies, v = 0;
                  v < m.length;
                  v++
                ) {
                  var y = m[v],
                    x = y.position.x - p.x,
                    w = y.position.y - p.y;
                  c.setPosition(y, {
                    x: p.x + x * f,
                    y: p.y + w * h,
                  }),
                    c.scale(y, f, h);
                }
                return u;
              }),
              (i.bounds = function (u) {
                for (
                  var f = i.allBodies(u), h = [], p = 0;
                  p < f.length;
                  p += 1
                ) {
                  var g = f[p];
                  h.push(g.bounds.min, g.bounds.max);
                }
                return l.create(h);
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(4),
            a = s(5),
            l = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i._motionWakeThreshold = 0.18),
              (i._motionSleepThreshold = 0.08),
              (i._minBias = 0.9),
              (i.update = function (c, u) {
                for (
                  var f = u / l._baseDelta, h = i._motionSleepThreshold, p = 0;
                  p < c.length;
                  p++
                ) {
                  var g = c[p],
                    m = o.getSpeed(g),
                    v = o.getAngularSpeed(g),
                    y = m * m + v * v;
                  if (g.force.x !== 0 || g.force.y !== 0) {
                    i.set(g, !1);
                    continue;
                  }
                  var x = Math.min(g.motion, y),
                    w = Math.max(g.motion, y);
                  (g.motion = i._minBias * x + (1 - i._minBias) * w),
                    g.sleepThreshold > 0 && g.motion < h
                      ? ((g.sleepCounter += 1),
                        g.sleepCounter >= g.sleepThreshold / f && i.set(g, !0))
                      : g.sleepCounter > 0 && (g.sleepCounter -= 1);
                }
              }),
              (i.afterCollisions = function (c) {
                for (
                  var u = i._motionSleepThreshold, f = 0;
                  f < c.length;
                  f++
                ) {
                  var h = c[f];
                  if (h.isActive) {
                    var p = h.collision,
                      g = p.bodyA.parent,
                      m = p.bodyB.parent;
                    if (
                      !(
                        (g.isSleeping && m.isSleeping) ||
                        g.isStatic ||
                        m.isStatic
                      ) &&
                      (g.isSleeping || m.isSleeping)
                    ) {
                      var v = g.isSleeping && !g.isStatic ? g : m,
                        y = v === g ? m : g;
                      !v.isStatic && y.motion > u && i.set(v, !1);
                    }
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.set = function (c, u) {
                var f = c.isSleeping;
                u
                  ? ((c.isSleeping = !0),
                    (c.sleepCounter = c.sleepThreshold),
                    (c.positionImpulse.x = 0),
                    (c.positionImpulse.y = 0),
                    (c.positionPrev.x = c.position.x),
                    (c.positionPrev.y = c.position.y),
                    (c.anglePrev = c.angle),
                    (c.speed = 0),
                    (c.angularSpeed = 0),
                    (c.motion = 0),
                    f || a.trigger(c, "sleepStart"))
                  : ((c.isSleeping = !1),
                    (c.sleepCounter = 0),
                    f && a.trigger(c, "sleepEnd"));
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(3),
            a = s(9);
          (function () {
            var l = [],
              c = {
                overlap: 0,
                axis: null,
              },
              u = {
                overlap: 0,
                axis: null,
              };
            (i.create = function (f, h) {
              return {
                pair: null,
                collided: !1,
                bodyA: f,
                bodyB: h,
                parentA: f.parent,
                parentB: h.parent,
                depth: 0,
                normal: {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                },
                tangent: {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                },
                penetration: {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                },
                supports: [null, null],
                supportCount: 0,
              };
            }),
              (i.collides = function (f, h, p) {
                if (
                  (i._overlapAxes(c, f.vertices, h.vertices, f.axes),
                  c.overlap <= 0 ||
                    (i._overlapAxes(u, h.vertices, f.vertices, h.axes),
                    u.overlap <= 0))
                )
                  return null;
                var g = p && p.table[a.id(f, h)],
                  m;
                g
                  ? (m = g.collision)
                  : ((m = i.create(f, h)),
                    (m.collided = !0),
                    (m.bodyA = f.id < h.id ? f : h),
                    (m.bodyB = f.id < h.id ? h : f),
                    (m.parentA = m.bodyA.parent),
                    (m.parentB = m.bodyB.parent)),
                  (f = m.bodyA),
                  (h = m.bodyB);
                var v;
                c.overlap < u.overlap ? (v = c) : (v = u);
                var y = m.normal,
                  x = m.tangent,
                  w = m.penetration,
                  _ = m.supports,
                  b = v.overlap,
                  T = v.axis,
                  E = T.x,
                  P = T.y,
                  N = h.position.x - f.position.x,
                  A = h.position.y - f.position.y;
                E * N + P * A >= 0 && ((E = -E), (P = -P)),
                  (y.x = E),
                  (y.y = P),
                  (x.x = -P),
                  (x.y = E),
                  (w.x = E * b),
                  (w.y = P * b),
                  (m.depth = b);
                var M = i._findSupports(f, h, y, 1),
                  j = 0;
                if (
                  (o.contains(f.vertices, M[0]) && (_[j++] = M[0]),
                  o.contains(f.vertices, M[1]) && (_[j++] = M[1]),
                  j < 2)
                ) {
                  var I = i._findSupports(h, f, y, -1);
                  o.contains(h.vertices, I[0]) && (_[j++] = I[0]),
                    j < 2 && o.contains(h.vertices, I[1]) && (_[j++] = I[1]);
                }
                return j === 0 && (_[j++] = M[0]), (m.supportCount = j), m;
              }),
              (i._overlapAxes = function (f, h, p, g) {
                var m = h.length,
                  v = p.length,
                  y = h[0].x,
                  x = h[0].y,
                  w = p[0].x,
                  _ = p[0].y,
                  b = g.length,
                  T = Number.MAX_VALUE,
                  E = 0,
                  P,
                  N,
                  A,
                  M,
                  j,
                  I;
                for (j = 0; j < b; j++) {
                  var z = g[j],
                    O = z.x,
                    L = z.y,
                    V = y * O + x * L,
                    $ = w * O + _ * L,
                    B = V,
                    D = $;
                  for (I = 1; I < m; I += 1)
                    (M = h[I].x * O + h[I].y * L),
                      M > B ? (B = M) : M < V && (V = M);
                  for (I = 1; I < v; I += 1)
                    (M = p[I].x * O + p[I].y * L),
                      M > D ? (D = M) : M < $ && ($ = M);
                  if (
                    ((N = B - $),
                    (A = D - V),
                    (P = N < A ? N : A),
                    P < T && ((T = P), (E = j), P <= 0))
                  )
                    break;
                }
                (f.axis = g[E]), (f.overlap = T);
              }),
              (i._findSupports = function (f, h, p, g) {
                var m = h.vertices,
                  v = m.length,
                  y = f.position.x,
                  x = f.position.y,
                  w = p.x * g,
                  _ = p.y * g,
                  b = m[0],
                  T = b,
                  E = w * (y - T.x) + _ * (x - T.y),
                  P,
                  N,
                  A;
                for (A = 1; A < v; A += 1)
                  (T = m[A]),
                    (N = w * (y - T.x) + _ * (x - T.y)),
                    N < E && ((E = N), (b = T));
                return (
                  (P = m[(v + b.index - 1) % v]),
                  (E = w * (y - P.x) + _ * (x - P.y)),
                  (T = m[(b.index + 1) % v]),
                  w * (y - T.x) + _ * (x - T.y) < E
                    ? ((l[0] = b), (l[1] = T), l)
                    : ((l[0] = b), (l[1] = P), l)
                );
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(16);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (a, l) {
              var c = a.bodyA,
                u = a.bodyB,
                f = {
                  id: i.id(c, u),
                  bodyA: c,
                  bodyB: u,
                  collision: a,
                  contacts: [o.create(), o.create()],
                  contactCount: 0,
                  separation: 0,
                  isActive: !0,
                  isSensor: c.isSensor || u.isSensor,
                  timeCreated: l,
                  timeUpdated: l,
                  inverseMass: 0,
                  friction: 0,
                  frictionStatic: 0,
                  restitution: 0,
                  slop: 0,
                };
              return i.update(f, a, l), f;
            }),
              (i.update = function (a, l, c) {
                var u = l.supports,
                  f = l.supportCount,
                  h = a.contacts,
                  p = l.parentA,
                  g = l.parentB;
                (a.isActive = !0),
                  (a.timeUpdated = c),
                  (a.collision = l),
                  (a.separation = l.depth),
                  (a.inverseMass = p.inverseMass + g.inverseMass),
                  (a.friction =
                    p.friction < g.friction ? p.friction : g.friction),
                  (a.frictionStatic =
                    p.frictionStatic > g.frictionStatic
                      ? p.frictionStatic
                      : g.frictionStatic),
                  (a.restitution =
                    p.restitution > g.restitution
                      ? p.restitution
                      : g.restitution),
                  (a.slop = p.slop > g.slop ? p.slop : g.slop),
                  (a.contactCount = f),
                  (l.pair = a);
                var m = u[0],
                  v = h[0],
                  y = u[1],
                  x = h[1];
                (x.vertex === m || v.vertex === y) &&
                  ((h[1] = v), (h[0] = v = x), (x = h[1])),
                  (v.vertex = m),
                  (x.vertex = y);
              }),
              (i.setActive = function (a, l, c) {
                l
                  ? ((a.isActive = !0), (a.timeUpdated = c))
                  : ((a.isActive = !1), (a.contactCount = 0));
              }),
              (i.id = function (a, l) {
                return a.id < l.id
                  ? a.id.toString(36) + ":" + l.id.toString(36)
                  : l.id.toString(36) + ":" + a.id.toString(36);
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(3),
            a = s(2),
            l = s(7),
            c = s(1),
            u = s(11),
            f = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i._warming = 0.4),
              (i._torqueDampen = 1),
              (i._minLength = 1e-6),
              (i.create = function (h) {
                var p = h;
                p.bodyA &&
                  !p.pointA &&
                  (p.pointA = {
                    x: 0,
                    y: 0,
                  }),
                  p.bodyB &&
                    !p.pointB &&
                    (p.pointB = {
                      x: 0,
                      y: 0,
                    });
                var g = p.bodyA ? a.add(p.bodyA.position, p.pointA) : p.pointA,
                  m = p.bodyB ? a.add(p.bodyB.position, p.pointB) : p.pointB,
                  v = a.magnitude(a.sub(g, m));
                (p.length = typeof p.length != "undefined" ? p.length : v),
                  (p.id = p.id || f.nextId()),
                  (p.label = p.label || "Constraint"),
                  (p.type = "constraint"),
                  (p.stiffness = p.stiffness || (p.length > 0 ? 1 : 0.7)),
                  (p.damping = p.damping || 0),
                  (p.angularStiffness = p.angularStiffness || 0),
                  (p.angleA = p.bodyA ? p.bodyA.angle : p.angleA),
                  (p.angleB = p.bodyB ? p.bodyB.angle : p.angleB),
                  (p.plugin = {});
                var y = {
                  visible: !0,
                  lineWidth: 2,
                  strokeStyle: "#ffffff",
                  type: "line",
                  anchors: !0,
                };
                return (
                  p.length === 0 && p.stiffness > 0.1
                    ? ((y.type = "pin"), (y.anchors = !1))
                    : p.stiffness < 0.9 && (y.type = "spring"),
                  (p.render = f.extend(y, p.render)),
                  p
                );
              }),
              (i.preSolveAll = function (h) {
                for (var p = 0; p < h.length; p += 1) {
                  var g = h[p],
                    m = g.constraintImpulse;
                  g.isStatic ||
                    (m.x === 0 && m.y === 0 && m.angle === 0) ||
                    ((g.position.x += m.x),
                    (g.position.y += m.y),
                    (g.angle += m.angle));
                }
              }),
              (i.solveAll = function (h, p) {
                for (
                  var g = f.clamp(p / f._baseDelta, 0, 1), m = 0;
                  m < h.length;
                  m += 1
                ) {
                  var v = h[m],
                    y = !v.bodyA || (v.bodyA && v.bodyA.isStatic),
                    x = !v.bodyB || (v.bodyB && v.bodyB.isStatic);
                  (y || x) && i.solve(h[m], g);
                }
                for (m = 0; m < h.length; m += 1)
                  (v = h[m]),
                    (y = !v.bodyA || (v.bodyA && v.bodyA.isStatic)),
                    (x = !v.bodyB || (v.bodyB && v.bodyB.isStatic)),
                    !y && !x && i.solve(h[m], g);
              }),
              (i.solve = function (h, p) {
                var g = h.bodyA,
                  m = h.bodyB,
                  v = h.pointA,
                  y = h.pointB;
                if (!(!g && !m)) {
                  g &&
                    !g.isStatic &&
                    (a.rotate(v, g.angle - h.angleA, v), (h.angleA = g.angle)),
                    m &&
                      !m.isStatic &&
                      (a.rotate(y, m.angle - h.angleB, y),
                      (h.angleB = m.angle));
                  var x = v,
                    w = y;
                  if (
                    (g && (x = a.add(g.position, v)),
                    m && (w = a.add(m.position, y)),
                    !(!x || !w))
                  ) {
                    var _ = a.sub(x, w),
                      b = a.magnitude(_);
                    b < i._minLength && (b = i._minLength);
                    var T = (b - h.length) / b,
                      E = h.stiffness >= 1 || h.length === 0,
                      P = E ? h.stiffness * p : h.stiffness * p * p,
                      N = h.damping * p,
                      A = a.mult(_, T * P),
                      M = (g ? g.inverseMass : 0) + (m ? m.inverseMass : 0),
                      j =
                        (g ? g.inverseInertia : 0) + (m ? m.inverseInertia : 0),
                      I = M + j,
                      z,
                      O,
                      L,
                      V,
                      $;
                    if (N > 0) {
                      var B = a.create();
                      (L = a.div(_, b)),
                        ($ = a.sub(
                          (m && a.sub(m.position, m.positionPrev)) || B,
                          (g && a.sub(g.position, g.positionPrev)) || B,
                        )),
                        (V = a.dot(L, $));
                    }
                    g &&
                      !g.isStatic &&
                      ((O = g.inverseMass / M),
                      (g.constraintImpulse.x -= A.x * O),
                      (g.constraintImpulse.y -= A.y * O),
                      (g.position.x -= A.x * O),
                      (g.position.y -= A.y * O),
                      N > 0 &&
                        ((g.positionPrev.x -= N * L.x * V * O),
                        (g.positionPrev.y -= N * L.y * V * O)),
                      (z =
                        (a.cross(v, A) / I) *
                        i._torqueDampen *
                        g.inverseInertia *
                        (1 - h.angularStiffness)),
                      (g.constraintImpulse.angle -= z),
                      (g.angle -= z)),
                      m &&
                        !m.isStatic &&
                        ((O = m.inverseMass / M),
                        (m.constraintImpulse.x += A.x * O),
                        (m.constraintImpulse.y += A.y * O),
                        (m.position.x += A.x * O),
                        (m.position.y += A.y * O),
                        N > 0 &&
                          ((m.positionPrev.x += N * L.x * V * O),
                          (m.positionPrev.y += N * L.y * V * O)),
                        (z =
                          (a.cross(y, A) / I) *
                          i._torqueDampen *
                          m.inverseInertia *
                          (1 - h.angularStiffness)),
                        (m.constraintImpulse.angle += z),
                        (m.angle += z));
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.postSolveAll = function (h) {
                for (var p = 0; p < h.length; p++) {
                  var g = h[p],
                    m = g.constraintImpulse;
                  if (
                    !(g.isStatic || (m.x === 0 && m.y === 0 && m.angle === 0))
                  ) {
                    l.set(g, !1);
                    for (var v = 0; v < g.parts.length; v++) {
                      var y = g.parts[v];
                      o.translate(y.vertices, m),
                        v > 0 && ((y.position.x += m.x), (y.position.y += m.y)),
                        m.angle !== 0 &&
                          (o.rotate(y.vertices, m.angle, g.position),
                          u.rotate(y.axes, m.angle),
                          v > 0 &&
                            a.rotateAbout(
                              y.position,
                              m.angle,
                              g.position,
                              y.position,
                            )),
                        c.update(y.bounds, y.vertices, g.velocity);
                    }
                    (m.angle *= i._warming),
                      (m.x *= i._warming),
                      (m.y *= i._warming);
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.pointAWorld = function (h) {
                return {
                  x:
                    (h.bodyA ? h.bodyA.position.x : 0) +
                    (h.pointA ? h.pointA.x : 0),
                  y:
                    (h.bodyA ? h.bodyA.position.y : 0) +
                    (h.pointA ? h.pointA.y : 0),
                };
              }),
              (i.pointBWorld = function (h) {
                return {
                  x:
                    (h.bodyB ? h.bodyB.position.x : 0) +
                    (h.pointB ? h.pointB.x : 0),
                  y:
                    (h.bodyB ? h.bodyB.position.y : 0) +
                    (h.pointB ? h.pointB.y : 0),
                };
              }),
              (i.currentLength = function (h) {
                var p =
                    (h.bodyA ? h.bodyA.position.x : 0) +
                    (h.pointA ? h.pointA.x : 0),
                  g =
                    (h.bodyA ? h.bodyA.position.y : 0) +
                    (h.pointA ? h.pointA.y : 0),
                  m =
                    (h.bodyB ? h.bodyB.position.x : 0) +
                    (h.pointB ? h.pointB.x : 0),
                  v =
                    (h.bodyB ? h.bodyB.position.y : 0) +
                    (h.pointB ? h.pointB.y : 0),
                  y = p - m,
                  x = g - v;
                return Math.sqrt(y * y + x * x);
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(2),
            a = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i.fromVertices = function (l) {
              for (var c = {}, u = 0; u < l.length; u++) {
                var f = (u + 1) % l.length,
                  h = o.normalise({
                    x: l[f].y - l[u].y,
                    y: l[u].x - l[f].x,
                  }),
                  p = h.y === 0 ? 1 / 0 : h.x / h.y;
                (p = p.toFixed(3).toString()), (c[p] = h);
              }

            }),
              (i.rotate = function (l, c) {
                if (c !== 0)
                  for (
                    var u = Math.cos(c), f = Math.sin(c), h = 0;
                    h < l.length;

                  ) {

                      (p.y = p.x * f + p.y * u),
                      (p.x = g);
                  }
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(3),
            a = s(0),
            l = s(4),

            u = s(2);
          (function () {
            (i.rectangle = function (f, h, p, g, m) {
              m = m || {};

                  x: f,

                  y.qualityMin,

                )),

              }

            }),
              (i.trapezoid = function (f, h, p, g, m, v) {
                (v = v || {}),

                  (m *= 0.5);

                };

                );
              }),
              (i.polygon = function (f, h, p, g, m) {
                if (((m = m || {}), p < 3)) return i.circle(f, h, g, m);
                for (
                  var v = (2 * Math.PI) / p, y = "", x = v * 0.5, w = 0;
                  w < p;
                  w += 1
                ) {
                  var _ = x + w * v,
                    b = Math.cos(_) * g,
                    T = Math.sin(_) * g;
                  y += "L " + b.toFixed(3) + " " + T.toFixed(3) + " ";

                  )),
