              }),
              (i.fromVertices = function (f, h, p, g, m, v, y, x) {
                var w = a.getDecomp(),
                  _,
                  b,
                  T,
                  E,
                  P,
                  N,
                  A,
                  M,
                  j,
                  I,
                  z;
                for (
                  _ = !!(w && w.quickDecomp),
                    g = g || {},
                    T = [],
                    m = typeof m != "undefined" ? m : !1,
                    v = typeof v != "undefined" ? v : 0.01,
                    y = typeof y != "undefined" ? y : 10,
                    x = typeof x != "undefined" ? x : 0.01,
                    a.isArray(p[0]) || (p = [p]),
                    I = 0;
                  I < p.length;
                  I += 1
                )
                  if (
                    ((N = p[I]),
                    (E = o.isConvex(N)),
                    (P = !E),
                    P &&
                      !_ &&
                      a.warnOnce(
                        "Bodies.fromVertices: Install the 'poly-decomp' library and use Common.setDecomp or provide 'decomp' as a global to decompose concave vertices.",
                      ),
                    E || !_)
                  )
                    E ? (N = o.clockwiseSort(N)) : (N = o.hull(N)),
                      T.push({
                        position: {
                          x: f,
                          y: h,
                        },
                        vertices: N,
                      });
                  else {
                    var O = N.map(function (W) {
                      return [W.x, W.y];
                    });
                    w.makeCCW(O),
                      v !== !1 && w.removeCollinearPoints(O, v),
                      x !== !1 &&
                        w.removeDuplicatePoints &&
                        w.removeDuplicatePoints(O, x);
                    var L = w.quickDecomp(O);
                    for (A = 0; A < L.length; A++) {
                      var V = L[A],
                        $ = V.map(function (W) {
                          return {
                            x: W[0],
                            y: W[1],
                          };
                        });
                      (y > 0 && o.area($) < y) ||
                        T.push({
                          position: o.centre($),
                          vertices: $,
                        });
                    }
                  }
                for (A = 0; A < T.length; A++)
                  T[A] = l.create(a.extend(T[A], g));
                if (m) {
                  var B = 5;
                  for (A = 0; A < T.length; A++) {
                    var D = T[A];
                    for (M = A + 1; M < T.length; M++) {
                      var R = T[M];
                      if (c.overlaps(D.bounds, R.bounds)) {
                        var U = D.vertices,
                          G = R.vertices;
                        for (j = 0; j < D.vertices.length; j++)
                          for (z = 0; z < R.vertices.length; z++) {
                            var K = u.magnitudeSquared(
                                u.sub(U[(j + 1) % U.length], G[z]),
                              ),
                              X = u.magnitudeSquared(
                                u.sub(U[j], G[(z + 1) % G.length]),
                              );
                            K < B &&
                              X < B &&
                              ((U[j].isInternal = !0), (G[z].isInternal = !0));
                          }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
                return T.length > 1
                  ? ((b = l.create(
                      a.extend(
                        {
                          parts: T.slice(0),
                        },
                        g,
                      ),
                    )),
                    l.setPosition(b, {
                      x: f,
                      y: h,
                    }),
                    b)
                  : T[0];
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(0),
            a = s(8);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (l) {
              var c = {
                bodies: [],
                collisions: [],
                pairs: null,
              };
              return o.extend(c, l);
            }),
              (i.setBodies = function (l, c) {
                l.bodies = c.slice(0);
              }),
              (i.clear = function (l) {
                (l.bodies = []), (l.collisions = []);
              }),
              (i.collisions = function (l) {
                var c = l.pairs,
                  u = l.bodies,
                  f = u.length,
                  h = i.canCollide,
                  p = a.collides,
                  g = l.collisions,
                  m = 0,
                  v,
                  y;
                for (u.sort(i._compareBoundsX), v = 0; v < f; v++) {
                  var x = u[v],
                    w = x.bounds,
                    _ = x.bounds.max.x,
                    b = x.bounds.max.y,
                    T = x.bounds.min.y,
                    E = x.isStatic || x.isSleeping,
                    P = x.parts.length,
                    N = P === 1;
                  for (y = v + 1; y < f; y++) {
                    var A = u[y],
                      M = A.bounds;
                    if (M.min.x > _) break;
                    if (
                      !(b < M.min.y || T > M.max.y) &&
                      !(E && (A.isStatic || A.isSleeping)) &&
                      h(x.collisionFilter, A.collisionFilter)
                    ) {
                      var j = A.parts.length;
                      if (N && j === 1) {
                        var I = p(x, A, c);
                        I && (g[m++] = I);
                      } else
                        for (
                          var z = P > 1 ? 1 : 0, O = j > 1 ? 1 : 0, L = z;
                          L < P;
                          L++
                        )
                          for (
                            var V = x.parts[L], w = V.bounds, $ = O;
                            $ < j;
                            $++
                          ) {
                            var B = A.parts[$],
                              M = B.bounds;
                            if (
                              !(
                                w.min.x > M.max.x ||
                                w.max.x < M.min.x ||
                                w.max.y < M.min.y ||
                                w.min.y > M.max.y
                              )
                            ) {
                              var I = p(V, B, c);
                              I && (g[m++] = I);
                            }
                          }
                    }
                  }
                }
                return g.length !== m && (g.length = m), g;
              }),
              (i.canCollide = function (l, c) {
                return l.group === c.group && l.group !== 0
                  ? l.group > 0
                  : (l.mask & c.category) !== 0 && (c.mask & l.category) !== 0;
              }),
              (i._compareBoundsX = function (l, c) {
                return l.bounds.min.x - c.bounds.min.x;
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (a) {
              var l = {};
              return (
                a ||
                  o.log(
                    "Mouse.create: element was undefined, defaulting to document.body",
                    "warn",
                  ),
                (l.element = a || document.body),
                (l.absolute = {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                }),
                (l.position = {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                }),
                (l.mousedownPosition = {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                }),
                (l.mouseupPosition = {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                }),
                (l.offset = {
                  x: 0,
                  y: 0,
                }),
                (l.scale = {
                  x: 1,
                  y: 1,
                }),
                (l.wheelDelta = 0),
                (l.button = -1),
                (l.pixelRatio =
                  parseInt(l.element.getAttribute("data-pixel-ratio"), 10) ||
                  1),
                (l.sourceEvents = {
                  mousemove: null,
                  mousedown: null,
                  mouseup: null,
                  mousewheel: null,
                }),
                (l.mousemove = function (c) {
                  var u = i._getRelativeMousePosition(
                      c,
                      l.element,
                      l.pixelRatio,
                    ),
                    f = c.changedTouches;
                  f && ((l.button = 0), c.preventDefault()),
                    (l.absolute.x = u.x),
                    (l.absolute.y = u.y),
                    (l.position.x = l.absolute.x * l.scale.x + l.offset.x),
                    (l.position.y = l.absolute.y * l.scale.y + l.offset.y),
                    (l.sourceEvents.mousemove = c);
                }),
                (l.mousedown = function (c) {
                  var u = i._getRelativeMousePosition(
                      c,
                      l.element,
                      l.pixelRatio,
                    ),
                    f = c.changedTouches;
                  f
                    ? ((l.button = 0), c.preventDefault())
                    : (l.button = c.button),
                    (l.absolute.x = u.x),
                    (l.absolute.y = u.y),
                    (l.position.x = l.absolute.x * l.scale.x + l.offset.x),
                    (l.position.y = l.absolute.y * l.scale.y + l.offset.y),
                    (l.mousedownPosition.x = l.position.x),
                    (l.mousedownPosition.y = l.position.y),
                    (l.sourceEvents.mousedown = c);
                }),
                (l.mouseup = function (c) {
                  var u = i._getRelativeMousePosition(
                      c,
                      l.element,
                      l.pixelRatio,
                    ),
                    f = c.changedTouches;
                  f && c.preventDefault(),
                    (l.button = -1),
                    (l.absolute.x = u.x),
                    (l.absolute.y = u.y),
                    (l.position.x = l.absolute.x * l.scale.x + l.offset.x),
                    (l.position.y = l.absolute.y * l.scale.y + l.offset.y),
                    (l.mouseupPosition.x = l.position.x),
                    (l.mouseupPosition.y = l.position.y),
                    (l.sourceEvents.mouseup = c);
                }),
                (l.mousewheel = function (c) {
                  (l.wheelDelta = Math.max(
                    -1,
                    Math.min(1, c.wheelDelta || -c.detail),
                  )),
                    c.preventDefault(),
                    (l.sourceEvents.mousewheel = c);
                }),
                i.setElement(l, l.element),
                l
              );
            }),
              (i.setElement = function (a, l) {
                (a.element = l),
                  l.addEventListener("mousemove", a.mousemove, {
                    passive: !0,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("mousedown", a.mousedown, {
                    passive: !0,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("mouseup", a.mouseup, {
                    passive: !0,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("wheel", a.mousewheel, {
                    passive: !1,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("touchmove", a.mousemove, {
                    passive: !1,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("touchstart", a.mousedown, {
                    passive: !1,
                  }),
                  l.addEventListener("touchend", a.mouseup, {
                    passive: !1,
                  });
              }),
              (i.clearSourceEvents = function (a) {
                (a.sourceEvents.mousemove = null),
                  (a.sourceEvents.mousedown = null),
                  (a.sourceEvents.mouseup = null),
                  (a.sourceEvents.mousewheel = null),
                  (a.wheelDelta = 0);
              }),
              (i.setOffset = function (a, l) {
                (a.offset.x = l.x),
                  (a.offset.y = l.y),
                  (a.position.x = a.absolute.x * a.scale.x + a.offset.x),
                  (a.position.y = a.absolute.y * a.scale.y + a.offset.y);
              }),
              (i.setScale = function (a, l) {
                (a.scale.x = l.x),
                  (a.scale.y = l.y),
                  (a.position.x = a.absolute.x * a.scale.x + a.offset.x),
                  (a.position.y = a.absolute.y * a.scale.y + a.offset.y);
              }),
              (i._getRelativeMousePosition = function (a, l, c) {
                var u = l.getBoundingClientRect(),
                  f =
                    document.documentElement ||
                    document.body.parentNode ||
                    document.body,
                  h =
                    window.pageXOffset !== void 0
                      ? window.pageXOffset
                      : f.scrollLeft,
                  p =
                    window.pageYOffset !== void 0
                      ? window.pageYOffset
                      : f.scrollTop,
                  g = a.changedTouches,
                  m,
                  v;
                return (
                  g
                    ? ((m = g[0].pageX - u.left - h),
                      (v = g[0].pageY - u.top - p))
                    : ((m = a.pageX - u.left - h), (v = a.pageY - u.top - p)),
                  {
                    x: m / ((l.clientWidth / (l.width || l.clientWidth)) * c),
                    y:
                      v / ((l.clientHeight / (l.height || l.clientHeight)) * c),
                  }
                );
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i._registry = {}),
              (i.register = function (a) {
                if (
                  (i.isPlugin(a) ||
                    o.warn(
                      "Plugin.register:",
                      i.toString(a),
                      "does not implement all required fields.",
                    ),
                  a.name in i._registry)
                ) {
                  var l = i._registry[a.name],
                    c = i.versionParse(a.version).number,
                    u = i.versionParse(l.version).number;
                  c > u
                    ? (o.warn(
                        "Plugin.register:",
                        i.toString(l),
                        "was upgraded to",
                        i.toString(a),
                      ),
                      (i._registry[a.name] = a))
                    : c < u
                      ? o.warn(
                          "Plugin.register:",
                          i.toString(l),
                          "can not be downgraded to",
                          i.toString(a),
                        )
                      : a !== l &&
                        o.warn(
                          "Plugin.register:",
                          i.toString(a),
                          "is already registered to different plugin object",
                        );
                } else i._registry[a.name] = a;
                return a;
              }),
              (i.resolve = function (a) {
                return i._registry[i.dependencyParse(a).name];
              }),
              (i.toString = function (a) {
                return typeof a == "string"
                  ? a
                  : (a.name || "anonymous") +
                      "@" +
                      (a.version || a.range || "0.0.0");
              }),
              (i.isPlugin = function (a) {
                return a && a.name && a.version && a.install;
              }),
              (i.isUsed = function (a, l) {
                return a.used.indexOf(l) > -1;
              }),
              (i.isFor = function (a, l) {
                var c = a.for && i.dependencyParse(a.for);
                return (
                  !a.for ||
                  (l.name === c.name && i.versionSatisfies(l.version, c.range))
                );
              }),
              (i.use = function (a, l) {
                if (
                  ((a.uses = (a.uses || []).concat(l || [])),
                  a.uses.length === 0)
                ) {
                  o.warn(
                    "Plugin.use:",
                    i.toString(a),
                    "does not specify any dependencies to install.",
                  );
                  return;
                }
                for (
                  var c = i.dependencies(a),
                    u = o.topologicalSort(c),
                    f = [],
                    h = 0;
                  h < u.length;
                  h += 1
                )
                  if (u[h] !== a.name) {
                    var p = i.resolve(u[h]);
                    if (!p) {
                      f.push(" " + u[h]);
                      continue;
                    }
                    i.isUsed(a, p.name) ||
                      (i.isFor(p, a) ||
                        (o.warn(
                          "Plugin.use:",
                          i.toString(p),
                          "is for",
                          p.for,
                          "but installed on",
                          i.toString(a) + ".",
                        ),
                        (p._warned = !0)),
                      p.install
                        ? p.install(a)
                        : (o.warn(
                            "Plugin.use:",
                            i.toString(p),
                            "does not specify an install function.",
                          ),
                          (p._warned = !0)),
                      p._warned
                        ? (f.push(" " + i.toString(p)), delete p._warned)
                        : f.push(" " + i.toString(p)),
                      a.used.push(p.name));
                  }
                f.length > 0 && o.info(f.join("  "));
              }),
              (i.dependencies = function (a, l) {
                var c = i.dependencyParse(a),
                  u = c.name;
                if (((l = l || {}), !(u in l))) {
                  (a = i.resolve(a) || a),
                    (l[u] = o.map(a.uses || [], function (h) {
                      i.isPlugin(h) && i.register(h);
                      var p = i.dependencyParse(h),
                        g = i.resolve(h);
                      return (
                        g && !i.versionSatisfies(g.version, p.range)
                          ? (o.warn(
                              "Plugin.dependencies:",
                              i.toString(g),
                              "does not satisfy",
                              i.toString(p),
                              "used by",
                              i.toString(c) + ".",
                            ),
                            (g._warned = !0),
                            (a._warned = !0))
                          : g ||
                            (o.warn(
                              "Plugin.dependencies:",
                              i.toString(h),
                              "used by",
                              i.toString(c),
                              "could not be resolved.",
                            ),
                            (a._warned = !0)),
                        p.name
                      );
                    }));
                  for (var f = 0; f < l[u].length; f += 1)
                    i.dependencies(l[u][f], l);
                  return l;
                }
              }),
              (i.dependencyParse = function (a) {
                if (o.isString(a)) {
                  var l =
                    /^[\w-]+(@(\*|[\^~]?\d+\.\d+\.\d+(-[0-9A-Za-z-+]+)?))?$/;
                  return (
                    l.test(a) ||
                      o.warn(
                        "Plugin.dependencyParse:",
                        a,
                        "is not a valid dependency string.",
                      ),
                    {
                      name: a.split("@")[0],
                      range: a.split("@")[1] || "*",
                    }
                  );
                }
                return {
                  name: a.name,
                  range: a.range || a.version,
                };
              }),
              (i.versionParse = function (a) {
                var l =
                  /^(\*)|(\^|~|>=|>)?\s*((\d+)\.(\d+)\.(\d+))(-[0-9A-Za-z-+]+)?$/;
                l.test(a) ||
                  o.warn(
                    "Plugin.versionParse:",
                    a,
                    "is not a valid version or range.",
                  );
                var c = l.exec(a),
                  u = Number(c[4]),
                  f = Number(c[5]),
                  h = Number(c[6]);
                return {
                  isRange: !!(c[1] || c[2]),
                  version: c[3],
                  range: a,
                  operator: c[1] || c[2] || "",
                  major: u,
                  minor: f,
                  patch: h,
                  parts: [u, f, h],
                  prerelease: c[7],
                  number: u * 1e8 + f * 1e4 + h,
                };
              }),
              (i.versionSatisfies = function (a, l) {
                l = l || "*";
                var c = i.versionParse(l),
                  u = i.versionParse(a);
                if (c.isRange) {
                  if (c.operator === "*" || a === "*") return !0;
                  if (c.operator === ">") return u.number > c.number;
                  if (c.operator === ">=") return u.number >= c.number;
                  if (c.operator === "~")
                    return (
                      u.major === c.major &&
                      u.minor === c.minor &&
                      u.patch >= c.patch
                    );
                  if (c.operator === "^")
                    return c.major > 0
                      ? u.major === c.major && u.number >= c.number
                      : c.minor > 0
                        ? u.minor === c.minor && u.patch >= c.patch
                        : u.patch === c.patch;
                }
                return a === l || a === "*";
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r) {
          var s = {};
          (n.exports = s),
            (function () {
              s.create = function (i) {
                return {
                  vertex: i,
                  normalImpulse: 0,
                  tangentImpulse: 0,
                };
              };
            })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(7),
            a = s(18),
            l = s(13),
            c = s(19),
            u = s(5),
            f = s(6),
            h = s(10),
            p = s(0),
            g = s(4);
          (function () {
            (i._deltaMax = 1e3 / 60),
              (i.create = function (m) {
                m = m || {};
                var v = {
                    positionIterations: 6,
                    velocityIterations: 4,
                    constraintIterations: 2,
                    enableSleeping: !1,
                    events: [],
                    plugin: {},
                    gravity: {
                      x: 0,
                      y: 1,
                      scale: 0.001,
                    },
                    timing: {
                      timestamp: 0,
                      timeScale: 1,
                      lastDelta: 0,
                      lastElapsed: 0,
                      lastUpdatesPerFrame: 0,
                    },
                  },
                  y = p.extend(v, m);
                return (
                  (y.world =
                    m.world ||
                    f.create({
                      label: "World",
                    })),
                  (y.pairs = m.pairs || c.create()),
                  (y.detector = m.detector || l.create()),
                  (y.detector.pairs = y.pairs),
                  (y.grid = {
                    buckets: [],
                  }),
                  (y.world.gravity = y.gravity),
                  (y.broadphase = y.grid),
                  (y.metrics = {}),
                  y
                );
              }),
              (i.update = function (m, v) {
                var y = p.now(),
                  x = m.world,
                  w = m.detector,
                  _ = m.pairs,
                  b = m.timing,
                  T = b.timestamp,
                  E;
                v > i._deltaMax &&
                  p.warnOnce(
                    "Matter.Engine.update: delta argument is recommended to be less than or equal to",
                    i._deltaMax.toFixed(3),
                    "ms.",
                  ),
                  (v = typeof v != "undefined" ? v : p._baseDelta),
                  (v *= b.timeScale),
                  (b.timestamp += v),
                  (b.lastDelta = v);
                var P = {
                  timestamp: b.timestamp,
                  delta: v,
                };
                u.trigger(m, "beforeUpdate", P);
                var N = f.allBodies(x),
                  A = f.allConstraints(x);
                for (
                  x.isModified &&
                    (l.setBodies(w, N), f.setModified(x, !1, !1, !0)),
                    m.enableSleeping && o.update(N, v),
                    i._bodiesApplyGravity(N, m.gravity),
                    v > 0 && i._bodiesUpdate(N, v),
                    u.trigger(m, "beforeSolve", P),
                    h.preSolveAll(N),
                    E = 0;
                  E < m.constraintIterations;
                  E++
                )
                  h.solveAll(A, v);
                h.postSolveAll(N);
                var M = l.collisions(w);
                c.update(_, M, T),
                  m.enableSleeping && o.afterCollisions(_.list),
                  _.collisionStart.length > 0 &&
                    u.trigger(m, "collisionStart", {
                      pairs: _.collisionStart,
                      timestamp: b.timestamp,
                      delta: v,
                    });
                var j = p.clamp(20 / m.positionIterations, 0, 1);
                for (
                  a.preSolvePosition(_.list), E = 0;
                  E < m.positionIterations;
                  E++
                )
                  a.solvePosition(_.list, v, j);
                for (
                  a.postSolvePosition(N), h.preSolveAll(N), E = 0;
                  E < m.constraintIterations;
                  E++
                )
                  h.solveAll(A, v);
                for (
                  h.postSolveAll(N), a.preSolveVelocity(_.list), E = 0;
                  E < m.velocityIterations;
                  E++
                )
                  a.solveVelocity(_.list, v);
                return (
                  i._bodiesUpdateVelocities(N),
                  _.collisionActive.length > 0 &&
                    u.trigger(m, "collisionActive", {
                      pairs: _.collisionActive,
                      timestamp: b.timestamp,
                      delta: v,
                    }),
                  _.collisionEnd.length > 0 &&
                    u.trigger(m, "collisionEnd", {
                      pairs: _.collisionEnd,
                      timestamp: b.timestamp,
                      delta: v,
                    }),
                  i._bodiesClearForces(N),
                  u.trigger(m, "afterUpdate", P),
                  (m.timing.lastElapsed = p.now() - y),
                  m
                );
              }),
              (i.merge = function (m, v) {
                if ((p.extend(m, v), v.world)) {
                  (m.world = v.world), i.clear(m);
                  for (var y = f.allBodies(m.world), x = 0; x < y.length; x++) {
                    var w = y[x];
                    o.set(w, !1), (w.id = p.nextId());
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.clear = function (m) {
                c.clear(m.pairs), l.clear(m.detector);
              }),
              (i._bodiesClearForces = function (m) {
                for (var v = m.length, y = 0; y < v; y++) {
                  var x = m[y];
                  (x.force.x = 0), (x.force.y = 0), (x.torque = 0);
                }
              }),
              (i._bodiesApplyGravity = function (m, v) {
                var y = typeof v.scale != "undefined" ? v.scale : 0.001,
                  x = m.length;
                if (!((v.x === 0 && v.y === 0) || y === 0))
                  for (var w = 0; w < x; w++) {
                    var _ = m[w];
                    _.isStatic ||
                      _.isSleeping ||
                      ((_.force.y += _.mass * v.y * y),
                      (_.force.x += _.mass * v.x * y));
                  }
              }),
              (i._bodiesUpdate = function (m, v) {
                for (var y = m.length, x = 0; x < y; x++) {
                  var w = m[x];
                  w.isStatic || w.isSleeping || g.update(w, v);
                }
              }),
              (i._bodiesUpdateVelocities = function (m) {
                for (var v = m.length, y = 0; y < v; y++)
                  g.updateVelocities(m[y]);
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(3),
            a = s(0),
            l = s(1);
          (function () {
            (i._restingThresh = 2),
              (i._restingThreshTangent = Math.sqrt(6)),
              (i._positionDampen = 0.9),
              (i._positionWarming = 0.8),
              (i._frictionNormalMultiplier = 5),
              (i._frictionMaxStatic = Number.MAX_VALUE),
              (i.preSolvePosition = function (c) {
                var u,
                  f,
                  h,
                  p = c.length;
                for (u = 0; u < p; u++)
                  (f = c[u]),
                    f.isActive &&
                      ((h = f.contactCount),
                      (f.collision.parentA.totalContacts += h),
                      (f.collision.parentB.totalContacts += h));
              }),
              (i.solvePosition = function (c, u, f) {
                var h,
                  p,
                  g,
                  m,
                  v,
                  y,
                  x,
                  w,
                  _ = i._positionDampen * (f || 1),
                  b = a.clamp(u / a._baseDelta, 0, 1),
                  T = c.length;
                for (h = 0; h < T; h++)
                  (p = c[h]),
                    !(!p.isActive || p.isSensor) &&
                      ((g = p.collision),
                      (m = g.parentA),
                      (v = g.parentB),
                      (y = g.normal),
                      (p.separation =
                        g.depth +
                        y.x * (v.positionImpulse.x - m.positionImpulse.x) +
                        y.y * (v.positionImpulse.y - m.positionImpulse.y)));
                for (h = 0; h < T; h++)
                  (p = c[h]),
                    !(!p.isActive || p.isSensor) &&
                      ((g = p.collision),
                      (m = g.parentA),
                      (v = g.parentB),
                      (y = g.normal),
                      (w = p.separation - p.slop * b),
                      (m.isStatic || v.isStatic) && (w *= 2),
                      m.isStatic ||
                        m.isSleeping ||
                        ((x = _ / m.totalContacts),
                        (m.positionImpulse.x += y.x * w * x),
                        (m.positionImpulse.y += y.y * w * x)),
                      v.isStatic ||
                        v.isSleeping ||
                        ((x = _ / v.totalContacts),
                        (v.positionImpulse.x -= y.x * w * x),
                        (v.positionImpulse.y -= y.y * w * x)));
              }),
              (i.postSolvePosition = function (c) {
                for (
                  var u = i._positionWarming,
                    f = c.length,
                    h = o.translate,
                    p = l.update,
                    g = 0;
                  g < f;
                  g++
                ) {
                  var m = c[g],
                    v = m.positionImpulse,
                    y = v.x,
                    x = v.y,
                    w = m.velocity;
                  if (((m.totalContacts = 0), y !== 0 || x !== 0)) {
                    for (var _ = 0; _ < m.parts.length; _++) {
                      var b = m.parts[_];
                      h(b.vertices, v),
                        p(b.bounds, b.vertices, w),
                        (b.position.x += y),
                        (b.position.y += x);
                    }
                    (m.positionPrev.x += y),
                      (m.positionPrev.y += x),
                      y * w.x + x * w.y < 0
                        ? ((v.x = 0), (v.y = 0))
                        : ((v.x *= u), (v.y *= u));
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.preSolveVelocity = function (c) {
                var u = c.length,
                  f,
                  h;
                for (f = 0; f < u; f++) {
                  var p = c[f];
                  if (!(!p.isActive || p.isSensor)) {
                    var g = p.contacts,
                      m = p.contactCount,
                      v = p.collision,
                      y = v.parentA,
                      x = v.parentB,
                      w = v.normal,
                      _ = v.tangent;
                    for (h = 0; h < m; h++) {
                      var b = g[h],
                        T = b.vertex,
                        E = b.normalImpulse,
                        P = b.tangentImpulse;
                      if (E !== 0 || P !== 0) {
                        var N = w.x * E + _.x * P,
                          A = w.y * E + _.y * P;
                        y.isStatic ||
                          y.isSleeping ||
                          ((y.positionPrev.x += N * y.inverseMass),
                          (y.positionPrev.y += A * y.inverseMass),
                          (y.anglePrev +=
                            y.inverseInertia *
                            ((T.x - y.position.x) * A -
                              (T.y - y.position.y) * N))),
                          x.isStatic ||
                            x.isSleeping ||
                            ((x.positionPrev.x -= N * x.inverseMass),
                            (x.positionPrev.y -= A * x.inverseMass),
                            (x.anglePrev -=
                              x.inverseInertia *
                              ((T.x - x.position.x) * A -
                                (T.y - x.position.y) * N)));
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.solveVelocity = function (c, u) {
                var f = u / a._baseDelta,
                  h = f * f,
                  p = h * f,
                  g = -i._restingThresh * f,
                  m = i._restingThreshTangent,
                  v = i._frictionNormalMultiplier * f,
                  y = i._frictionMaxStatic,
                  x = c.length,
                  w,
                  _,
                  b,
                  T;
                for (b = 0; b < x; b++) {
                  var E = c[b];
                  if (!(!E.isActive || E.isSensor)) {
                    var P = E.collision,
                      N = P.parentA,
                      A = P.parentB,
                      M = P.normal.x,
                      j = P.normal.y,
                      I = P.tangent.x,
                      z = P.tangent.y,
                      O = E.inverseMass,
                      L = E.friction * E.frictionStatic * v,
                      V = E.contacts,
                      $ = E.contactCount,
                      B = 1 / $,
                      D = N.position.x - N.positionPrev.x,
                      R = N.position.y - N.positionPrev.y,
                      U = N.angle - N.anglePrev,
                      G = A.position.x - A.positionPrev.x,
                      K = A.position.y - A.positionPrev.y,
                      X = A.angle - A.anglePrev;
                    for (T = 0; T < $; T++) {
                      var W = V[T],
                        Q = W.vertex,
                        Y = Q.x - N.position.x,
                        ne = Q.y - N.position.y,
                        ee = Q.x - A.position.x,
                        J = Q.y - A.position.y,
                        H = D - ne * U,
                        te = R + Y * U,
                        oe = G - J * X,
                        _e = K + ee * X,
                        le = H - oe,
                        ue = te - _e,
                        ae = M * le + j * ue,
                        be = I * le + z * ue,
                        Ze = E.separation + ae,
                        Qe = Math.min(Ze, 1);
                      Qe = Ze < 0 ? 0 : Qe;
                      var Re = Qe * L;
                      be < -Re || be > Re
                        ? ((_ = be > 0 ? be : -be),
                          (w = E.friction * (be > 0 ? 1 : -1) * p),
                          w < -_ ? (w = -_) : w > _ && (w = _))
                        : ((w = be), (_ = y));
                      var Tt = Y * j - ne * M,
                        Mt = ee * j - J * M,
                        mn =
                          B /
                          (O +
                            N.inverseInertia * Tt * Tt +
                            A.inverseInertia * Mt * Mt),
                        $t = (1 + E.restitution) * ae * mn;
                      if (((w *= mn), ae < g)) W.normalImpulse = 0;
                      else {
                        var Lt = W.normalImpulse;
                        (W.normalImpulse += $t),
                          W.normalImpulse > 0 && (W.normalImpulse = 0),
                          ($t = W.normalImpulse - Lt);
                      }
                      if (be < -m || be > m) W.tangentImpulse = 0;
                      else {
                        var kn = W.tangentImpulse;
                        (W.tangentImpulse += w),
                          W.tangentImpulse < -_ && (W.tangentImpulse = -_),
                          W.tangentImpulse > _ && (W.tangentImpulse = _),
                          (w = W.tangentImpulse - kn);
                      }
                      var Ft = M * $t + I * w,
                        zt = j * $t + z * w;
                      N.isStatic ||
                        N.isSleeping ||
                        ((N.positionPrev.x += Ft * N.inverseMass),
                        (N.positionPrev.y += zt * N.inverseMass),
                        (N.anglePrev += (Y * zt - ne * Ft) * N.inverseInertia)),
                        A.isStatic ||
                          A.isSleeping ||
                          ((A.positionPrev.x -= Ft * A.inverseMass),
                          (A.positionPrev.y -= zt * A.inverseMass),
                          (A.anglePrev -=
                            (ee * zt - J * Ft) * A.inverseInertia));
                    }
                  }
                }
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(9),
            a = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (l) {
              return a.extend(
                {
                  table: {},
                  list: [],
                  collisionStart: [],
                  collisionActive: [],
                  collisionEnd: [],
                },
                l,
              );
            }),
              (i.update = function (l, c, u) {
                var f = o.update,
                  h = o.create,
                  p = o.setActive,
                  g = l.table,
                  m = l.list,
                  v = m.length,
                  y = v,
                  x = l.collisionStart,
                  w = l.collisionEnd,
                  _ = l.collisionActive,
                  b = c.length,
                  T = 0,
                  E = 0,
                  P = 0,
                  N,
                  A,
                  M;
                for (M = 0; M < b; M++)
                  (N = c[M]),
                    (A = N.pair),
                    A
                      ? (A.isActive && (_[P++] = A), f(A, N, u))
                      : ((A = h(N, u)),
                        (g[A.id] = A),
                        (x[T++] = A),
                        (m[y++] = A));
                for (y = 0, v = m.length, M = 0; M < v; M++)
                  (A = m[M]),
                    A.timeUpdated >= u
                      ? (m[y++] = A)
                      : (p(A, !1, u),
                        A.collision.bodyA.sleepCounter > 0 &&
                        A.collision.bodyB.sleepCounter > 0
                          ? (m[y++] = A)
                          : ((w[E++] = A), delete g[A.id]));
                m.length !== y && (m.length = y),
                  x.length !== T && (x.length = T),
                  w.length !== E && (w.length = E),
                  _.length !== P && (_.length = P);
              }),
              (i.clear = function (l) {
                return (
                  (l.table = {}),
                  (l.list.length = 0),
                  (l.collisionStart.length = 0),
                  (l.collisionActive.length = 0),
                  (l.collisionEnd.length = 0),
                  l
                );
              });
          })();
        },

        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;

            a = s(10),

            f = l.deprecated;
          (function () {
            (i.stack = function (h, p, g, m, v, y, x) {
              for (
                var w = o.create({
                    label: "Stack",
                  }),
                  _ = h,
                  b = p,
                  T,
                  E = 0,
                  P = 0;
                P < m;
                P++
              ) {
                for (var N = 0, A = 0; A < g; A++) {
                  var M = x(_, b, A, P, T, E);
                  if (M) {
                    var j = M.bounds.max.y - M.bounds.min.y,
                      I = M.bounds.max.x - M.bounds.min.x;
                    j > N && (N = j),
                      c.translate(M, {
                        x: I * 0.5,
                        y: j * 0.5,
                      }),
                      (_ = M.bounds.max.x + v),
                      o.addBody(w, M),
                      (T = M),
                      (E += 1);
                  } else _ += v;
                }
                (b += N + y), (_ = h);
              }
              return w;
            }),
              (i.chain = function (h, p, g, m, v, y) {
                for (var x = h.bodies, w = 1; w < x.length; w++) {
                  var _ = x[w - 1],
                    b = x[w],

              }),
              (i.mesh = function (h, p, g, m, v) {

                            },
                            v,
                          ),
                        ),
                      );
                  if (x > 0)
                    for (w = 0; w < p; w++)
                      (_ = y[w + (x - 1) * p]),
                        (b = y[w + x * p]),
                        o.addConstraint(

                          a.create(

                              {
                                bodyA: _,
                                bodyB: b,
                              },
                              v,
                            ),
                          ),

                            a.create(

                            ),
                          ));
                }
                return (h.label += " Mesh"), h;
              }),
              (i.pyramid = function (h, p, g, m, v, y, x) {
                return i.stack(h, p, g, m, v, y, function (w, _, b, T, E, P) {
                  var N = Math.min(m, Math.ceil(g / 2)),
                    A = E ? E.bounds.max.x - E.bounds.min.x : 0;
                  if (!(T > N)) {
                    T = N - T;
                    var M = T,
                      j = g - 1 - T;
                    if (!(b < M || b > j)) {
                      P === 1 &&
                        c.translate(E, {
                          x: (b + (g % 2 === 1 ? 1 : -1)) * A,
                          y: 0,
                        });
                      var I = E ? b * A : 0;
                      return x(h + I + b * v, _, b, T, E, P);
                    }
                  }
                });
              }),
              (i.newtonsCradle = function (h, p, g, m, v) {
                for (
                  var y = o.create({
                      label: "Newtons Cradle",
                    }),
                    x = 0;
                  x < g;
                  x++
                ) {

                }

                i,

                "Composites.newtonsCradle  moved to newtonsCradle example",
              ),
              (i.car = function (h, p, g, m, v) {
                var y = c.nextGroup(!0),
                  x = 20,

                return (

                  o.addConstraint(T, A),
                  o.addConstraint(T, M),
                  T
                );
              }),
              f(i, "car", "Composites.car  moved to car example"),
              (i.softBody = function (h, p, g, m, v, y, x, w, _, b) {
                (_ = l.extend(
                  {

                  _,
                )),

        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(9),
            a = s(0),
            l = a.deprecated;
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (c) {
              var u = {
                buckets: {},
                pairs: {},
                pairsList: [],
                bucketWidth: 48,
                bucketHeight: 48,
              };
              return a.extend(u, c);
            }),
              (i.update = function (c, u, f, h) {
                var p,
                  g,
                  m,
                  v = f.world,
                  y = c.buckets,
                  x,
                  w,
                  _ = !1;
                for (p = 0; p < u.length; p++) {
                  var b = u[p];
                  if (
                    !(b.isSleeping && !h) &&
                    !(
                      v.bounds &&
                      (b.bounds.max.x < v.bounds.min.x ||
                        b.bounds.min.x > v.bounds.max.x ||
                        b.bounds.max.y < v.bounds.min.y ||
                        b.bounds.min.y > v.bounds.max.y)
                    )
                  ) {
                    var T = i._getRegion(c, b);
                    if (!b.region || T.id !== b.region.id || h) {
                      (!b.region || h) && (b.region = T);
                      var E = i._regionUnion(T, b.region);
                      for (g = E.startCol; g <= E.endCol; g++)
                        for (m = E.startRow; m <= E.endRow; m++) {
                          (w = i._getBucketId(g, m)), (x = y[w]);
                          var P =
                              g >= T.startCol &&

                              g >= b.region.startCol &&
                              g <= b.region.endCol &&
                              m >= b.region.startRow &&

                          !P && N && N && x && i._bucketRemoveBody(c, x, b),
                            (b.region === T || (P && !N) || h) &&
                              (x || (x = i._createBucket(y, w)),
                              i._bucketAddBody(c, x, b));
                        }
                      (b.region = T), (_ = !0);
                    }
                  }
                }
                _ && (c.pairsList = i._createActivePairsList(c));
              }),

                (c.buckets = {}), (c.pairs = {}), (c.pairsList = []);
              }),
              l(i, "clear", "Grid.clear  replaced by Matter.Detector"),
              (i._regionUnion = function (c, u) {
                var f = Math.min(c.startCol, u.startCol),
                  h = Math.max(c.endCol, u.endCol),
                  p = Math.min(c.startRow, u.startRow),
                  g = Math.max(c.endRow, u.endRow);
                return i._createRegion(f, h, p, g);
              }),
              (i._getRegion = function (c, u) {
                var f = u.bounds,
                  h = Math.floor(f.min.x / c.bucketWidth),
                  p = Math.floor(f.max.x / c.bucketWidth),
                  g = Math.floor(f.min.y / c.bucketHeight),
                  m = Math.floor(f.max.y / c.bucketHeight);
                return i._createRegion(h, p, g, m);
              }),
              (i._createRegion = function (c, u, f, h) {
                return {
                  id: c + "," + u + "," + f + "," + h,
                  startCol: c,
                  endCol: u,
                  startRow: f,
                  endRow: h,
                };
              }),
              (i._getBucketId = function (c, u) {
                return "C" + c + "R" + u;
              }),
              (i._createBucket = function (c, u) {
                var f = (c[u] = []);
                return f;
              }),
              (i._bucketAddBody = function (c, u, f) {
                var h = c.pairs,
                  p = o.id,
                  g = u.length,
                  m;
                for (m = 0; m < g; m++) {
                  var v = u[m];
                  if (!(f.id === v.id || (f.isStatic && v.isStatic))) {
                    var y = p(f, v),
                      x = h[y];
                    x ? (x[2] += 1) : (h[y] = [f, v, 1]);
                  }
                }
                u.push(f);
              }),
              (i._bucketRemoveBody = function (c, u, f) {
                var h = c.pairs,
                  p = o.id,
                  g;
                u.splice(a.indexOf(u, f), 1);
                var m = u.length;
                for (g = 0; g < m; g++) {
                  var v = h[p(f, u[g])];
                  v && (v[2] -= 1);
                }
              }),
              (i._createActivePairsList = function (c) {
                var u,
                  f = c.pairs,
                  h = a.keys(f),
                  p = h.length,
                  g = [],
                  m;
                for (m = 0; m < p; m++)
                  (u = f[h[m]]), u[2] > 0 ? g.push(u) : delete f[h[m]];
                return g;
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(3),
            a = s(7),
            l = s(14),
            c = s(5),
            u = s(13),
            f = s(10),
            h = s(6),
            p = s(0),
            g = s(1);
          (function () {
            (i.create = function (m, v) {
              var y = (m ? m.mouse : null) || (v ? v.mouse : null);
              y ||
                (m && m.render && m.render.canvas
                  ? (y = l.create(m.render.canvas))
                  : v && v.element
                    ? (y = l.create(v.element))
                    : ((y = l.create()),
                      p.warn(
                        "MouseConstraint.create: options.mouse was undefined, options.element was undefined, may not function as expected",
                      )));
              var x = f.create({
                  label: "Mouse Constraint",
                  pointA: y.position,
                  pointB: {
                    x: 0,
                    y: 0,
                  },
                  length: 0.01,
                  stiffness: 0.1,
                  angularStiffness: 1,
                  render: {
                    strokeStyle: "#90EE90",
                    lineWidth: 3,
                  },
                }),
                w = {
                  type: "mouseConstraint",
                  mouse: y,
                  element: null,
                  body: null,
                  constraint: x,
                  collisionFilter: {
                    category: 1,
                    mask: 4294967295,
                    group: 0,
                  },
                },
                _ = p.extend(w, v);
              return (
                c.on(m, "beforeUpdate", function () {
                  var b = h.allBodies(m.world);
                  i.update(_, b), i._triggerEvents(_);
                }),
                _
              );
            }),
              (i.update = function (m, v) {
                var y = m.mouse,
                  x = m.constraint,
                  w = m.body;
                if (y.button === 0) {
                  if (x.bodyB) a.set(x.bodyB, !1), (x.pointA = y.position);
                  else
                    for (var _ = 0; _ < v.length; _++)
                      if (
                        ((w = v[_]),
                        g.contains(w.bounds, y.position) &&
                          u.canCollide(w.collisionFilter, m.collisionFilter))
                      )
                        for (
                          var b = w.parts.length > 1 ? 1 : 0;
                          b < w.parts.length;
                          b++
                        ) {
                          var T = w.parts[b];
                          if (o.contains(T.vertices, y.position)) {
                            (x.pointA = y.position),
                              (x.bodyB = m.body = w),
                              (x.pointB = {
                                x: y.position.x - w.position.x,
                                y: y.position.y - w.position.y,
                              }),
                              (x.angleB = w.angle),
                              a.set(w, !1),
                              c.trigger(m, "startdrag", {
                                mouse: y,
                                body: w,
                              });
                            break;
                          }
                        }
                } else
                  (x.bodyB = m.body = null),
                    (x.pointB = null),
                    w &&
                      c.trigger(m, "enddrag", {
                        mouse: y,
                        body: w,
                      });
              }),
              (i._triggerEvents = function (m) {
                var v = m.mouse,
                  y = v.sourceEvents;
                y.mousemove &&
                  c.trigger(m, "mousemove", {
                    mouse: v,
                  }),
                  y.mousedown &&
                    c.trigger(m, "mousedown", {
                      mouse: v,
                    }),
                  y.mouseup &&
                    c.trigger(m, "mouseup", {
                      mouse: v,
                    }),
                  l.clearSourceEvents(v);
              });
          })();
        },
        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;
          var o = s(2),
            a = s(8),
            l = s(1),
            c = s(12),
            u = s(3);
          (function () {
            (i.collides = function (f, h) {
              for (
                var p = [],
                  g = h.length,
                  m = f.bounds,
                  v = a.collides,
                  y = l.overlaps,
                  x = 0;
                x < g;
                x++
              ) {
                var w = h[x],
                  _ = w.parts.length,
                  b = _ === 1 ? 0 : 1;
                if (y(w.bounds, m))
                  for (var T = b; T < _; T++) {
                    var E = w.parts[T];
                    if (y(E.bounds, m)) {
                      var P = v(E, f);
                      if (P) {
                        p.push(P);
                        break;
                      }
                    }
                  }
              }
              return p;
            }),
              (i.ray = function (f, h, p, g) {
                g = g || 1e-100;
                for (
                  var m = o.angle(h, p),
                    v = o.magnitude(o.sub(h, p)),
                    y = (p.x + h.x) * 0.5,
                    x = (p.y + h.y) * 0.5,
                    w = c.rectangle(y, x, v, g, {
                      angle: m,
                    }),
                    _ = i.collides(w, f),
                    b = 0;
                  b < _.length;
                  b += 1
                ) {
                  var T = _[b];
                  T.body = T.bodyB = T.bodyA;
                }
                return _;
              }),
              (i.region = function (f, h, p) {
                for (var g = [], m = 0; m < f.length; m++) {
                  var v = f[m],
                    y = l.overlaps(v.bounds, h);
                  ((y && !p) || (!y && p)) && g.push(v);
                }
                return g;
              }),
              (i.point = function (f, h) {
                for (var p = [], g = 0; g < f.length; g++) {
                  var m = f[g];
                  if (l.contains(m.bounds, h))
                    for (
                      var v = m.parts.length === 1 ? 0 : 1;
                      v < m.parts.length;
                      v++
                    ) {
                      var y = m.parts[v];
                      if (
                        l.contains(y.bounds, h) &&
                        u.contains(y.vertices, h)
                      ) {
                        p.push(m);
                        break;
                      }
                    }
                }
                return p;
              });
          })();
        },

                  E
                );

                  (b.frameRequestId = p(T)),

              }),
              (i.stop = function (b) {
                g(b.frameRequestId);
              }),
              (i.setPixelRatio = function (b, T) {

              }),

                  (b.bounds.max.y = b.bounds.min.y + E),

              }),
              (i.lookAt = function (b, T, E, P) {
                (P = typeof P != "undefined" ? P : !0),
                  (T = a.isArray(T) ? T : [T]),
                  (E = E || {
                    x: 0,
                    y: 0,
                  });
                for (

                  (b.bounds.max.y = N.min.y + O * R),
                  P &&
                    ((b.bounds.min.x += z * 0.5 - z * D * 0.5),
                    (b.bounds.max.x += z * 0.5 - z * D * 0.5),
                    (b.bounds.min.y += O * 0.5 - O * R * 0.5),
                    (b.bounds.max.y += O * 0.5 - O * R * 0.5)),

                  (b.bounds.min.y -= E.y),
                  (b.bounds.max.y -= E.y),

                    }),
                    h.setOffset(b.mouse, b.bounds.min));
              }),
              (i.startViewTransform = function (b) {

                  0,
                  b.options.pixelRatio / N,
                  0,

                ),

              }),
              (i.endViewTransform = function (b) {
                b.context.setTransform(
                  b.options.pixelRatio,
                  0,
                  0,
                  b.options.pixelRatio,
                  0,
                  0,
                );
              }),
              (i.world = function (b, T) {
                var E = a.now(),
                  P = b.engine,
                  N = P.world,
                  A = b.canvas,
                  M = b.context,
                  j = b.options,
                  I = b.timing,
                  z = l.allBodies(N),
                  O = l.allConstraints(N),
                  L = j.wireframes ? j.wireframeBackground : j.background,
                  V = [],
                  $ = [],

                  D = {
                    timestamp: P.timing.timestamp,
                  };
                if (
                  (u.trigger(b, "beforeRender", D),
                  b.currentBackground !== L && _(b, L),
                  (M.globalCompositeOperation = "source-in"),
                  (M.fillStyle = "transparent"),
                  M.fillRect(0, 0, A.width, A.height),
                  (M.globalCompositeOperation = "source-over"),
                  j.hasBounds)
                ) {
                  for (B = 0; B < z.length; B++) {

                      K && (W = f.add(K.position, U.pointB)),

                        (c.contains(b.bounds, X) || c.contains(b.bounds, W)) &&
                        $.push(U);
                  }

                      (h.setScale(b.mouse, {

                    i.bodyWireframes(b, V, M)),
                  j.showBounds && i.bodyBounds(b, V, M),
                  (j.showAxes || j.showAngleIndicator) && i.bodyAxes(b, V, M),
                  j.showPositions && i.bodyPositions(b, V, M),
                  j.showVelocity && i.bodyVelocity(b, V, M),
                  j.showIds && i.bodyIds(b, V, M),
                  j.showSeparations && i.separations(b, P.pairs.list, M),
                  j.showCollisions && i.collisions(b, P.pairs.list, M),
                  j.showVertexNumbers && i.vertexNumbers(b, V, M),
                  j.showMousePosition && i.mousePosition(b, b.mouse, M),
                  i.constraints($, M),
                  j.hasBounds && i.endViewTransform(b),
                  u.trigger(b, "afterRender", D),
                  (I.lastElapsed = a.now() - E);
              }),
              (i.stats = function (b, T, E) {
                for (
                  var P = b.engine,
                    N = P.world,
                    A = l.allBodies(N),
                    M = 0,
                    j = 55,
                    I = 44,
                    z = 0,
                    O = 0,
                    L = 0;
                  L < A.length;
                  L += 1
                )
                  M += A[L].parts.length;
                var V = {
                  Part: M,
                  Body: A.length,
                  Cons: l.allConstraints(N).length,
                  Comp: l.allComposites(N).length,
                  Pair: P.pairs.list.length,
                };

                }
              }),
              (i.performance = function (b, T) {
                var E = b.engine,
                  P = b.timing,
                  N = P.deltaHistory,
                  A = P.elapsedHistory,
                  M = P.timestampElapsedHistory,
                  j = P.engineDeltaHistory,

                  z = P.engineElapsedHistory,
                  O = E.timing.lastUpdatesPerFrame,
                  L = E.timing.lastDelta,
                  V = v(N),
                  $ = v(A),
                  B = v(j),
                  D = v(I),
                  R = v(z),
                  U = v(M),
                  G = U / V || 0,

                  X = 1e3 / V || 0,

                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    N.length,
                    Math.round(X) + " fps",
                    X / i._goodFps,
                    function (H) {
                      return N[H] / V - 1;
                    },
                  ),
                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee + Q + Y,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    j.length,
                    L.toFixed(2) + " dt",
                    i._goodDelta / L,
                    function (H) {
                      return j[H] / B - 1;
                    },
                  ),
                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee + (Q + Y) * 2,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    I.length,
                    O + " upf",
                    Math.pow(a.clamp(D / K || 1, 0, 1), 4),
                    function (H) {
                      return I[H] / D - 1;
                    },
                  ),
                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee + (Q + Y) * 3,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    z.length,

                    1 - (O * R) / i._goodFps,
                    function (H) {
                      return z[H] / R - 1;
                    },
                  ),
                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee + (Q + Y) * 4,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    A.length,
                    $.toFixed(2) + " rt",
                    1 - $ / i._goodFps,
                    function (H) {
                      return A[H] / $ - 1;
                    },
                  ),
                  i.status(
                    T,
                    ee + (Q + Y) * 5,
                    J,
                    Y,
                    W,
                    M.length,
                    G.toFixed(2) + " x",
                    G * G * G,
                    function (H) {
                      return (M[H] / N[H] / G || 0) - 1;
                    },
                  );
              }),
              (i.status = function (b, T, E, P, N, A, M, j, I) {
                (b.strokeStyle = "#888"),
                  (b.fillStyle = "#444"),
                  (b.lineWidth = 1),
                  b.fillRect(T, E + 7, P, 1),
                  b.beginPath(),
                  b.moveTo(T, E + 7 - N * a.clamp(0.4 * I(0), -2, 2));

                    T + z,
                    E + 7 - (z < A ? N * a.clamp(0.4 * I(z), -2, 2) : 0),
                  );
                b.stroke(),
                  (b.fillStyle =
                    "hsl(" + a.clamp(25 + 95 * j, 0, 120) + ",100%,60%)"),
                  b.fillRect(T, E - 7, 4, 4),
                  (b.font = "12px Arial"),
                  (b.textBaseline = "middle"),
                  (b.textAlign = "right"),
                  (b.fillStyle = "#eee"),
                  b.fillText(M, T + P, E - 5);
              }),
              (i.constraints = function (b, T) {
                for (var E = T, P = 0; P < b.length; P++) {
                  var N = b[P];

                    var A = N.bodyA,
                      M = N.bodyB,

                      I;

                      (A ? (j = f.add(A.position, N.pointA)) : (j = N.pointA),

                    )

                        E.arc(j.x, j.y, 3, 0, 2 * Math.PI),
                        E.closePath();

                        (M ? (I = f.add(M.position, N.pointB)) : (I = N.pointB),

                      )
                        for (

                            O = f.perp(f.normalise(z)),

                          $ < L;
                          $ += 1
                        )

                              j.y + z.y * ($ / L) + O.y * V * 4,
                            );
                      E.lineTo(I.x, I.y);
                    }
                    N.render.lineWidth &&
                      ((E.lineWidth = N.render.lineWidth),
                      (E.strokeStyle = N.render.strokeStyle),
                      E.stroke()),
                      N.render.anchors &&
                        ((E.fillStyle = N.render.strokeStyle),
                        E.beginPath(),
                        E.arc(j.x, j.y, 3, 0, 2 * Math.PI),
                        E.arc(I.x, I.y, 3, 0, 2 * Math.PI),
                        E.closePath(),
                        E.fill());
                  }
                }
              }),
              (i.bodies = function (b, T, E) {
                var P = E;
                b.engine;
                var N = b.options,
                  A = N.showInternalEdges || !N.wireframes,
                  M,
                  j,
                  I,
                  z;
                for (I = 0; I < T.length; I++)
                  if (((M = T[I]), !!M.render.visible)) {
                    for (
                      z = M.parts.length > 1 ? 1 : 0;
                      z < M.parts.length;
                      z++
                    )
                      if (((j = M.parts[z]), !!j.render.visible)) {
                        if (
                          (N.showSleeping && M.isSleeping
                            ? (P.globalAlpha = 0.5 * j.render.opacity)
                            : j.render.opacity !== 1 &&
                              (P.globalAlpha = j.render.opacity),
                          j.render.sprite &&
                            j.render.sprite.texture &&
                            !N.wireframes)
                        ) {
                          var O = j.render.sprite,
                            L = w(b, O.texture);
                          P.translate(j.position.x, j.position.y),
                            P.rotate(j.angle),
                            P.drawImage(
                              L,
                              L.width * -O.xOffset * O.xScale,
                              L.height * -O.yOffset * O.yScale,
                              L.width * O.xScale,
                              L.height * O.yScale,
                            ),
                            P.rotate(-j.angle),
                            P.translate(-j.position.x, -j.position.y);
                        } else {
                          if (j.circleRadius)
                            P.beginPath(),
                              P.arc(
                                j.position.x,
                                j.position.y,
                                j.circleRadius,
                                0,
                                2 * Math.PI,
                              );
                          else {
                            P.beginPath(),
                              P.moveTo(j.vertices[0].x, j.vertices[0].y);
                            for (var V = 1; V < j.vertices.length; V++)
                              !j.vertices[V - 1].isInternal || A
                                ? P.lineTo(j.vertices[V].x, j.vertices[V].y)
                                : P.moveTo(j.vertices[V].x, j.vertices[V].y),
                                j.vertices[V].isInternal &&
                                  !A &&
                                  P.moveTo(
                                    j.vertices[(V + 1) % j.vertices.length].x,
                                    j.vertices[(V + 1) % j.vertices.length].y,
                                  );
                            P.lineTo(j.vertices[0].x, j.vertices[0].y),
                              P.closePath();
                          }
                          N.wireframes
                            ? ((P.lineWidth = 1),
                              (P.strokeStyle = b.options.wireframeStrokeStyle),
                              P.stroke())
                            : ((P.fillStyle = j.render.fillStyle),
                              j.render.lineWidth &&

        function (n, r, s) {
          var i = {};
          n.exports = i;

            a = s(17),
            l = s(0);
          (function () {
            (i._maxFrameDelta = 1e3 / 15),
              (i._frameDeltaFallback = 1e3 / 60),
              (i._timeBufferMargin = 1.5),
              (i._elapsedNextEstimate = 1),
              (i._smoothingLowerBound = 0.1),
              (i._smoothingUpperBound = 0.9),
              (i.create = function (u) {
                var f = {
                    delta: 16.666666666666668,
                    frameDelta: null,
                    frameDeltaSmoothing: !0,
                    frameDeltaSnapping: !0,
                    frameDeltaHistory: [],
                    frameDeltaHistorySize: 100,
                    frameRequestId: null,
                    timeBuffer: 0,

                    lastUpdatesDeferred: 0,

                  },
                  h = l.extend(f, u);
                return (h.fps = 0), h;
              }),
              (i.run = function (u, f) {
                return (
                  (u.timeBuffer = i._frameDeltaFallback),
                  (function h(p) {
                    (u.frameRequestId = i._onNextFrame(u, h)),
                      p && u.enabled && i.tick(u, f, p);
                  })(),
                  u
                );
              }),
              (i.tick = function (u, f, h) {
                var p = l.now(),
                  g = u.delta,
                  m = 0,
                  v = h - u.timeLastTick;
                if (
                  ((!v ||
                    !u.timeLastTick ||
                    v > Math.max(i._maxFrameDelta, u.maxFrameTime)) &&
                    (v = u.frameDelta || i._frameDeltaFallback),
                  u.frameDeltaSmoothing)
                ) {
                  u.frameDeltaHistory.push(v),
                    (u.frameDeltaHistory = u.frameDeltaHistory.slice(
                      -u.frameDeltaHistorySize,
                    ));
                  var y = u.frameDeltaHistory.slice(0).sort(),
                    x = u.frameDeltaHistory.slice(
                      y.length * i._smoothingLowerBound,
                      y.length * i._smoothingUpperBound,
                    ),
                    w = c(x);
                  v = w || v;
                }
                u.frameDeltaSnapping && (v = 1e3 / Math.round(1e3 / v)),
                  (u.frameDelta = v),
                  (u.timeLastTick = h),
                  (u.timeBuffer += u.frameDelta),
                  (u.timeBuffer = l.clamp(
                    u.timeBuffer,
                    0,
                    u.frameDelta + g * i._timeBufferMargin,
                  )),
                  (u.lastUpdatesDeferred = 0);
                var _ = u.maxUpdates || Math.ceil(u.maxFrameTime / g),
                  b = {
                    timestamp: f.timing.timestamp,
                  };
                o.trigger(u, "beforeTick", b), o.trigger(u, "tick", b);
                for (
                  var T = l.now();
                  g > 0 && u.timeBuffer >= g * i._timeBufferMargin;

                ) {
                  o.trigger(u, "beforeUpdate", b),
                    a.update(f, g),
                    o.trigger(u, "afterUpdate", b),
                    (u.timeBuffer -= g),
                    (m += 1);
                  var E = l.now() - p,
                    P = l.now() - T,
                    N = E + (i._elapsedNextEstimate * P) / m;
                  if (m >= _ || N > u.maxFrameTime) {
                    u.lastUpdatesDeferred = Math.round(
                      Math.max(0, u.timeBuffer / g - i._timeBufferMargin),
                    );
                    break;
                  }
                }
                (f.timing.lastUpdatesPerFrame = m),
                  o.trigger(u, "afterTick", b),
                  u.frameDeltaHistory.length >= 100 &&
                    (u.lastUpdatesDeferred && Math.round(u.frameDelta / g) > _
                      ? l.warnOnce(
                          "Matter.Runner: runner reached runner.maxUpdates, see docs.",
                        )
                      : u.lastUpdatesDeferred &&
                        l.warnOnce(
                          "Matter.Runner: runner reached runner.maxFrameTime, see docs.",
                        ),
                    typeof u.isFixed != "undefined" &&
                      l.warnOnce(
                        "Matter.Runner: runner.isFixed is now redundant, see docs.",
                      ),
                    (u.deltaMin || u.deltaMax) &&
                      l.warnOnce(
                        "Matter.Runner: runner.deltaMin and runner.deltaMax were removed, see docs.",
                      ),
                    u.fps !== 0 &&
                      l.warnOnce(
                        "Matter.Runner: runner.fps was replaced by runner.delta, see docs.",
                      ));
              }),
              (i.stop = function (u) {
                i._cancelNextFrame(u);
              }),
              (i._onNextFrame = function (u, f) {
                if (
                  typeof window != "undefined" &&
                  window.requestAnimationFrame
                )
                  u.frameRequestId = window.requestAnimationFrame(f);
                else
                  throw new Error(
                    "Matter.Runner: missing required global window.requestAnimationFrame.",
                  );

                  );

            };
          })();
